            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Arnold, Thomas.</b>—Beowulf. A heroic poem of the eighth century. London, 1876. With English translation. Prose.</p></div></div>"
        },
