            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Æschere</b>.—Confidential friend of King Hrothgar. Elder brother of Yrmenlaf. Killed by Grendel.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003548\">21 <span class=\"smaller\">3</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005244\">30 <span class=\"smaller\">89</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Beanstan</b>.—Father of Breca.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001806\">9 <span class=\"smaller\">26</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Beowulf</b>.—Son of Scyld, the founder of the dynasty of Scyldings. Father of Healfdene, and grandfather of Hrothgar.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000669\">1 <span class=\"smaller\">18</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000759\">2 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Beowulf</b>.—The hero of the poem. Sprung from the stock of Geats, son of Ecgtheow. Brought up by his maternal grandfather Hrethel, and figuring in manhood as a devoted liegeman of his uncle Higelac. A hero from his youth. Has the strength of thirty men. Engages in a swimming-match with Breca. Goes to the help of Hrothgar against the monster Grendel. Vanquishes Grendel and his mother. Afterwards becomes king of the Geats. Late in life attempts to kill a fire-spewing dragon, and is slain. Is buried with great honors. His memorial mound.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001399\">6 <span class=\"smaller\">26</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001466\">7 <span class=\"smaller\">2</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001480\">7 <span class=\"smaller\">9</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001760\">9 <span class=\"smaller\">3</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001770\">9 <span class=\"smaller\">8</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002268\">12 <span class=\"smaller\">28</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002298\">12 <span class=\"smaller\">43</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003860\">23 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>, etc.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Breca</b>.—Beowulf’s opponent in the famous swimming-match.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001770\">9 <span class=\"smaller\">8</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001792\">9 <span class=\"smaller\">19</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001796\">9 <span class=\"smaller\">21</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001798\">9 <span class=\"smaller\">22</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Brondings</b>.—A people ruled by Breca.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001800\">9 <span class=\"smaller\">23</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Brosinga mene</b>.—A famous collar once owned by the Brosings.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003266\">19 <span class=\"smaller\">7</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Cain</b>.—Progenitor of Grendel and other monsters.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000869\">2 <span class=\"smaller\">56</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003406\">20 <span class=\"smaller\">11</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Dæghrefn</b>.—A warrior of the Hugs, killed by Beowulf.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006053\">35 <span class=\"smaller\">40</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Danes</b>.—Subjects of Scyld and his descendants, and hence often called Scyldings. Other names for them are Victory-Scyldings, Honor-Scyldings, Armor-Danes, Bright-Danes, East-Danes, West-Danes, North-Danes, South-Danes, Ingwins, Hrethmen.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000635\">1 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000759\">2 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000899\">3 <span class=\"smaller\">2</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001241\">5 <span class=\"smaller\">14</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001464\">7 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>, etc.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Ecglaf</b>.—Father of Unferth, who taunts Beowulf.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001756\">9 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Ecgtheow</b>.—Father of Beowulf, the hero of the poem. A widely-known Wægmunding warrior. Marries Hrethel’s daughter. After slaying Heatholaf, a Wylfing, he flees his country.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001468\">7 <span class=\"smaller\">3</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001225\">5 <span class=\"smaller\">6</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001658\">8 <span class=\"smaller\">4</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Ecgwela</b>.—A king of the Danes before Scyld.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004363\">25 <span class=\"smaller\">60</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Elan</b>.—Sister of Hrothgar, and probably wife of Ongentheow, king of the Swedes.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000777\">2 <span class=\"smaller\">10</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Eagle Cape</b>.—A promontory in Geat-land, under which took place Beowulf’s last encounter.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007148\">41 <span class=\"smaller\">87</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Eadgils</b>.—Son of Ohthere and brother of Eanmund.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005830\">34 <span class=\"smaller\">2</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Eanmund</b>.—Son of Ohthere and brother of Eadgils. The reference to these brothers is vague, and variously understood. Heyne supposes as follows: Raising a revolt against their father, they are obliged to leave Sweden. They go to the land of the Geats; with what intention, is not known, but probably to conquer and plunder. The Geatish king, Heardred, is slain by one of the brothers, probably Eanmund.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006277\">36 <span class=\"smaller\">10</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005406\">31 <span class=\"smaller\">54</span></$link> to <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005418\">31 <span class=\"smaller\">60</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005792\">33 <span class=\"smaller\">66</span></$link> to <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005838\">34 <span class=\"smaller\">6</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Eofor</b>.—A Geatish hero who slays Ongentheow in war, and is rewarded by Hygelac with the hand of his only daughter.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007010\">41 <span class=\"smaller\">18</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007070\">41 <span class=\"smaller\">48</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Eormenric</b>.—A Gothic king, from whom Hama took away the famous Brosinga mene.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003270\">19 <span class=\"smaller\">9</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Eomær</b>.—Son of Offa and Thrytho, king and queen of the Angles.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004885\">28 <span class=\"smaller\">69</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Finn</b>.—King of the North-Frisians and the Jutes. Marries Hildeburg. At his court takes place the horrible slaughter in which the Danish general, Hnæf, fell. Later on, Finn himself is slain by Danish warriors.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002985\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">18</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003009\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">30</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003037\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">44</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003113\">18 <span class=\"smaller\">4</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003151\">18 <span class=\"smaller\">23</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Fin-land</b>.—The country to which Beowulf was driven by the currents in his swimming-match.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001928\">10 <span class=\"smaller\">22</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Fitela</b>.—Son and nephew of King Sigemund, whose praises are sung in XIV.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002571\">14 <span class=\"smaller\">42</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002593\">14 <span class=\"smaller\">53</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Folcwalda</b>.—Father of Finn.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003025\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">38</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Franks</b>.—Introduced occasionally in referring to the death of Higelac.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003290\">19 <span class=\"smaller\">19</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006906\">40 <span class=\"smaller\">21</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006912\">40 <span class=\"smaller\">24</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Frisians</b>.—A part of them are ruled by Finn. Some of them were engaged in the struggle in which Higelac was slain.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002989\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">20</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003033\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">42</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003053\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">52</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006906\">40 <span class=\"smaller\">21</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Freaware</b>.—Daughter of King Hrothgar. Married to Ingeld, a Heathobard prince.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005029\">29 <span class=\"smaller\">60</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005130\">30 <span class=\"smaller\">32</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Froda</b>.—King of the Heathobards, and father of Ingeld.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005033\">29 <span class=\"smaller\">62</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Garmund</b>.—Father of Offa.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004889\">28 <span class=\"smaller\">71</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Geats, Geatmen</b>.—The race to which the hero of the poem belongs. Also called Weder-Geats, or Weders, War-Geats, Sea-Geats. They are ruled by Hrethel, Hæthcyn, Higelac, and Beowulf.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001073\">4 <span class=\"smaller\">7</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001470\">7 <span class=\"smaller\">4</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001974\">10 <span class=\"smaller\">45</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002118\">11 <span class=\"smaller\">8</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004623\">27 <span class=\"smaller\">14</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004763\">28 <span class=\"smaller\">8</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Gepids</b>.—Named in connection with the Danes and Swedes.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006041\">35 <span class=\"smaller\">34</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Grendel</b>.—A monster of the race of Cain. Dwells in the fens and moors. Is furiously envious when he hears sounds of joy in Hrothgar’s palace. Causes the king untold agony for years. Is finally conquered by Beowulf, and dies of his wound. His hand and arm are hung up in Hrothgar’s hall Heorot. His head is cut off by Beowulf when he goes down to fight with Grendel’s mother.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000857\">2 <span class=\"smaller\">50</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000897\">3 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000921\">3 <span class=\"smaller\">13</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001688\">8 <span class=\"smaller\">19</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002136\">11 <span class=\"smaller\">17</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002216\">12 <span class=\"smaller\">2</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002441\">13 <span class=\"smaller\">27</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002685\">15 <span class=\"smaller\">3</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Guthlaf</b>.—A Dane of Hnæf’s party.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003153\">18 <span class=\"smaller\">24</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Half-Danes</b>.—Branch of the Danes to which Hnæf belonged.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002987\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">19</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Halga</b>.—Surnamed the Good. Younger brother of Hrothgar.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000775\">2 <span class=\"smaller\">9</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hama</b>.—Takes the Brosinga mene from Eormenric.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003266\">19 <span class=\"smaller\">7</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hæreth</b>.—Father of Higelac’s queen, Hygd.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004825\">28 <span class=\"smaller\">39</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004945\">29 <span class=\"smaller\">18</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hæthcyn</b>.—Son of Hrethel and brother of Higelac. Kills his brother Herebeald accidentally. Is slain at Ravenswood, fighting against Ongentheow.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005912\">34 <span class=\"smaller\">43</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006019\">35 <span class=\"smaller\">23</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006928\">40 <span class=\"smaller\">32</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Helmings</b>.—The race to which Queen Wealhtheow belonged.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002010\">10 <span class=\"smaller\">63</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Heming</b>.—A kinsman of Garmund, perhaps nephew.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004855\">28 <span class=\"smaller\">54</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004887\">28 <span class=\"smaller\">70</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hengest</b>.—A Danish leader. Takes command on the fall of Hnæf.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003015\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">33</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003031\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">41</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Herebeald</b>.—Eldest son of Hrethel, the Geatish king, and brother of Higelac. Killed by his younger brother Hæthcyn.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005912\">34 <span class=\"smaller\">43</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005920\">34 <span class=\"smaller\">47</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Heremod</b>.—A Danish king of a dynasty before the Scylding line. Was a source of great sorrow to his people.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002615\">14 <span class=\"smaller\">64</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004361\">25 <span class=\"smaller\">59</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hereric</b>.—Referred to as uncle of Heardred, but otherwise unknown.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005418\">31 <span class=\"smaller\">60</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hetwars</b>.—Another name for the Franks.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005762\">33 <span class=\"smaller\">51</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Healfdene</b>.—Grandson of Scyld and father of Hrothgar. Ruled the Danes long and well.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000767\">2 <span class=\"smaller\">5</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001061\">4 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001678\">8 <span class=\"smaller\">14</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Heardred</b>.—Son of Higelac and Hygd, king and queen of the Geats. Succeeds his father, with Beowulf as regent. Is slain by the sons of Ohthere.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005410\">31 <span class=\"smaller\">56</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005786\">33 <span class=\"smaller\">63</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005810\">33 <span class=\"smaller\">75</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Heathobards</b>.—Race of Lombards, of which Froda is king. After Froda falls in battle with the Danes, Ingeld, his son, marries Hrothgar’s daughter, Freaware, in order to heal the feud.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005068\">30 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005078\">30 <span class=\"smaller\">6</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Heatholaf</b>.—A Wylfing warrior slain by Beowulf’s father.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001660\">8 <span class=\"smaller\">5</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Heathoremes</b>.—The people on whose shores Breca is cast by the waves during his contest with Beowulf.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001796\">9 <span class=\"smaller\">21</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Heorogar</b>.—Elder brother of Hrothgar, and surnamed ‘<span class=\"ang\">Weoroda Ræswa</span>,’ Prince of the Troopers.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000775\">2 <span class=\"smaller\">9</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001674\">8 <span class=\"smaller\">12</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hereward</b>.—Son of the above.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005332\">31 <span class=\"smaller\">17</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Heort</b>, <b>Heorot</b>.—The great mead-hall which King Hrothgar builds. It is invaded by Grendel for twelve years. Finally cleansed by Beowulf, the Geat. It is called Heort on account of the hart-antlers which decorate it.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000807\">2 <span class=\"smaller\">25</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000959\">3 <span class=\"smaller\">32</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000999\">3 <span class=\"smaller\">52</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hildeburg</b>.—Wife of Finn, daughter of Hoce, and related to Hnæf,—probably his sister.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002991\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">21</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003173\">18 <span class=\"smaller\">34</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hnæf</b>.—Leader of a branch of the Danes called Half-Danes. Killed in the struggle at Finn’s castle.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002987\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">19</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003071\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">61</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hondscio</b>.—One of Beowulf’s companions. Killed by Grendel just before Beowulf grappled with that monster.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005152\">30 <span class=\"smaller\">43</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hoce</b>.—Father of Hildeburg and probably of Hnæf.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003001\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">26</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hrethel</b>.—King of the Geats, father of Higelac, and grandfather of Beowulf.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001470\">7 <span class=\"smaller\">4</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005904\">34 <span class=\"smaller\">39</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hrethla</b>.—Once used for Hrethel.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001626\">7 <span class=\"smaller\">82</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hrethmen</b>.—Another name for the Danes.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001608\">7 <span class=\"smaller\">73</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hrethric</b>.—Son of Hrothgar.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003235\">18 <span class=\"smaller\">65</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004633\">27 <span class=\"smaller\">19</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hreosna-beorh</b>.—A promontory in Geat-land, near which Ohthere’s sons made plundering raids.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006009\">35 <span class=\"smaller\">18</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hrothgar</b>.—The Danish king who built the hall Heort, but was long unable to enjoy it on account of Grendel’s persecutions. Marries Wealhtheow, a Helming lady. Has two sons and a daughter. Is a typical Teutonic king, lavish of gifts. A devoted liegelord, as his lamentations over slain liegemen prove. Also very appreciative of kindness, as is shown by his loving gratitude to Beowulf.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000775\">2 <span class=\"smaller\">9</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000781\">2 <span class=\"smaller\">12</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001061\">4 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001670\">8 <span class=\"smaller\">10</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002681\">15 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>; etc., etc.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hrothmund</b>.—Son of Hrothgar.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003235\">18 <span class=\"smaller\">65</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hrothulf</b>.—Probably a son of Halga, younger brother of Hrothgar. Certainly on terms of close intimacy in Hrothgar’s palace.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002875\">16 <span class=\"smaller\">26</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003219\">18 <span class=\"smaller\">57</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hrunting</b>.—Unferth’s sword, lent to Beowulf.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003822\">22 <span class=\"smaller\">71</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004261\">25 <span class=\"smaller\">9</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hugs</b>.—A race in alliance with the Franks and Frisians at the time of Higelac’s fall.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006055\">35 <span class=\"smaller\">41</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hun</b>.—A Frisian warrior, probably general of the Hetwars. Gives Hengest a beautiful sword.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003143\">18 <span class=\"smaller\">19</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hunferth</b>.—Sometimes used for Unferth.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hygelac</b>, <b>Higelac</b>.—King of the Geats, uncle and liegelord of Beowulf, the hero of the poem.—His second wife is the lovely Hygd, daughter of Hæreth. The son of their union is Heardred. Is slain in a war with the Hugs, Franks, and Frisians combined. Beowulf is regent, and afterwards king of the Geats.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001071\">4 <span class=\"smaller\">6</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001221\">5 <span class=\"smaller\">4</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004815\">28 <span class=\"smaller\">34</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004927\">29 <span class=\"smaller\">9</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004951\">29 <span class=\"smaller\">21</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005410\">31 <span class=\"smaller\">56</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Hygd</b>.—Wife of Higelac, and daughter of Hæreth. There are some indications that she married Beowulf after she became a widow.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004821\">28 <span class=\"smaller\">37</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Ingeld</b>.—Son of the Heathobard king, Froda. Marries Hrothgar’s daughter, Freaware, in order to reconcile the two peoples.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005033\">29 <span class=\"smaller\">62</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005130\">30 <span class=\"smaller\">32</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Ingwins</b>.—Another name for the Danes.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002927\">16 <span class=\"smaller\">52</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003522\">20 <span class=\"smaller\">69</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Jutes</b>.—Name sometimes applied to Finn’s people.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002993\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">22</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003025\">17 <span class=\"smaller\">38</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003139\">18 <span class=\"smaller\">17</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Lafing</b>.—Name of a famous sword presented to Hengest by Hun.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003143\">18 <span class=\"smaller\">19</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Merewing</b>.—A Frankish king, probably engaged in the war in which Higelac was slain.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006922\">40 <span class=\"smaller\">29</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Nægling</b>.—Beowulf’s sword.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006409\">36 <span class=\"smaller\">76</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Offa</b>.—King of the Angles, and son of Garmund. Marries the terrible Thrytho who is so strongly contrasted with Hygd.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004865\">28 <span class=\"smaller\">59</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004879\">28 <span class=\"smaller\">66</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Ohthere</b>.—Son of Ongentheow, king of the Swedes. He is father of Eanmund and Eadgils.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006934\">40 <span class=\"smaller\">35</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006942\">40 <span class=\"smaller\">39</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Onela</b>.—Brother of Ohthere.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006287\">36 <span class=\"smaller\">15</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006942\">40 <span class=\"smaller\">39</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Ongentheow</b>.—King of Sweden, of the Scylfing dynasty. Married, perhaps, Elan, daughter of Healfdene.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006025\">35 <span class=\"smaller\">26</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007006\">41 <span class=\"smaller\">16</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Oslaf</b>.—A Dane of Hnæf’s party.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003153\">18 <span class=\"smaller\">24</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Ravenswood</b>.—The forest near which Hæthcyn was slain.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006926\">40 <span class=\"smaller\">31</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006946\">40 <span class=\"smaller\">41</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Scefing</b>.—Applied (<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000641\">1 <span class=\"smaller\">4</span></$link>) to Scyld, and meaning ‘son of Scef.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Scyld</b>.—Founder of the dynasty to which Hrothgar, his father, and grandfather belonged. He dies, and his body is put on a vessel, and set adrift. He goes from Daneland just as he had come to it—in a bark.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000641\">1 <span class=\"smaller\">4</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000671\">1 <span class=\"smaller\">19</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000687\">1 <span class=\"smaller\">27</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Scyldings</b>.—The descendants of Scyld. They are also called Honor-Scyldings, Victory-Scyldings, War-Scyldings, etc. (See ‘Danes,’ above.)—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000759\">2 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001464\">7 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001652\">8 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Scylfings</b>.—A Swedish royal line to which Wiglaf belonged.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006261\">36 <span class=\"smaller\">2</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Sigemund</b>.—Son of Wæls, and uncle and father of Fitela. His struggle with a dragon is related in connection with Beowulf’s deeds of prowess.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002563\">14 <span class=\"smaller\">38</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002581\">14 <span class=\"smaller\">47</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Swerting</b>.—Grandfather of Higelac, and father of Hrethel.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003274\">19 <span class=\"smaller\">11</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Swedes</b>.—People of Sweden, ruled by the Scylfings.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005999\">35 <span class=\"smaller\">13</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Thrytho</b>.—Wife of Offa, king of the Angles. Known for her fierce and unwomanly disposition. She is introduced as a contrast to the gentle Hygd, queen of Higelac.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004831\">28 <span class=\"smaller\">42</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004859\">28 <span class=\"smaller\">56</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Unferth</b>.—Son of Ecglaf, and seemingly a confidential courtier of Hrothgar. Taunts Beowulf for having taken part in the swimming-match. Lends Beowulf his sword when he goes to look for Grendel’s mother. In the MS. sometimes written <i>Hunferth</i>. <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001756\">9 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003187\">18 <span class=\"smaller\">41</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Wæls</b>.—Father of Sigemund.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000002607\">14 <span class=\"smaller\">60</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Wægmunding</b>.—A name occasionally applied to Wiglaf and Beowulf, and perhaps derived from a common ancestor, Wægmund.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006269\">36 <span class=\"smaller\">6</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006693\">38 <span class=\"smaller\">61</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Weders</b>.—Another name for Geats or Wedergeats.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Wayland</b>.—A fabulous smith mentioned in this poem and in other old Teutonic literature.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001628\">7 <span class=\"smaller\">83</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Wendels</b>.—The people of Wulfgar, Hrothgar’s messenger and retainer. (Perhaps = Vandals.)—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001407\">6 <span class=\"smaller\">30</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Wealhtheow</b>.—Wife of Hrothgar. Her queenly courtesy is well shown in the poem.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001994\">10 <span class=\"smaller\">55</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Weohstan</b>, or <b>Wihstan</b>.—A Wægmunding, and father of Wiglaf.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006259\">36 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Whale’s Ness</b>.—A prominent promontory, on which Beowulf’s mound was built.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006675\">38 <span class=\"smaller\">52</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007370\">42 <span class=\"smaller\">76</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Wiglaf</b>.—Son of Wihstan, and related to Beowulf. He remains faithful to Beowulf in the fatal struggle with the fire-drake. Would rather die than leave his lord in his dire emergency.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006259\">36 <span class=\"smaller\">1</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006263\">36 <span class=\"smaller\">3</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006313\">36 <span class=\"smaller\">28</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Wonred</b>.—Father of Wulf and Eofor.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007014\">41 <span class=\"smaller\">20</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007026\">41 <span class=\"smaller\">26</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Wulf</b>.—Son of Wonred. Engaged in the battle between Higelac’s and Ongentheow’s forces, and had a hand-to-hand fight with Ongentheow himself. Ongentheow disables him, and is thereupon slain by Eofor.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007012\">41 <span class=\"smaller\">19</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007032\">41 <span class=\"smaller\">29</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\"><p><b>Wulfgar</b>.—Lord of the Wendels, and retainer of Hrothgar.—<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001383\">6 <span class=\"smaller\">18</span></$link>; <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001407\">6 <span class=\"smaller\">30</span></$link>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
