            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000823\">[1]</$link> R. and t. B. prefer ‘<span class=\"ang\">ellor-gæst</span>’ to ‘<span class=\"ang\">ellen-gæst</span>’ (86): <i>Then the stranger from afar endured, etc.</i></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000885",
