        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000855\">[2]</$link> Some authorities would translate ‘<i>demon</i>’ instead of ‘<i>stranger</i>.’</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000859\">[3]</$link> Some authorities arrange differently, and render: <i>Who dwelt in the moor-fens, the marsh and the fastness, the land of the giant-race.</i></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
