        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Grendel attacks the sleeping heroes</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When the sun was sunken, he set out to visit</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The lofty hall-building, how the Ring-Danes had used it</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For beds and benches when the banquet was over.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then he found there reposing many a noble</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Asleep after supper; sorrow the heroes,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001044\">1</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Misery knew not. The monster of evil</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Greedy and cruel tarried but little,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">He drags off thirty of them, and devours them</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fell and frantic, and forced from their slumbers</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Thirty of thanemen; thence he departed</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Leaping and laughing, his lair to return to,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With surfeit of slaughter sallying homeward.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In the dusk of the dawning, as the day was just breaking,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Was Grendel’s prowess revealed to the warriors:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">A cry of agony goes up, when Grendel’s horrible deed is fully realized.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then, his meal-taking finished, a moan was uplifted,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Morning-cry mighty. The man-ruler famous,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The long-worthy atheling, sat very woful,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Suffered great sorrow, sighed for his liegemen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When they had seen the track of the hateful pursuer,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The spirit accursèd: too crushing that sorrow,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The monster returns the next night.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Too loathsome and lasting. Not longer he tarried,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">But one night after continued his slaughter</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Shameless and shocking, shrinking but little</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">From malice and murder; they mastered him fully.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He was easy to find then who otherwhere looked for</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A pleasanter place of repose in the lodges,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A bed in the bowers. Then was brought to his notice</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Told him truly by token apparent</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The hall-thane’s hatred: he held himself after</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Further and faster who the foeman did baffle.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\"><sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001046\">2</$link></sup>So ruled he and strongly strove against justice</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Lone against all men, till empty uptowered</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">King Hrothgar’s agony and suspense last twelve years.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The choicest of houses. Long was the season:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Twelve-winters’ time torture suffered</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The friend of the Scyldings, every affliction,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Endless agony; hence it after<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001048\">3</$link></sup> became</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Certainly known to the children of men</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sadly in measures, that long against Hrothgar</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Grendel struggled:—his grudges he cherished,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Murderous malice, many a winter,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Strife unremitting, and peacefully wished he</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\"><sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001050\">4</$link></sup>Life-woe to lift from no liegeman at all of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The men of the Dane-folk, for money to settle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">No counsellor needed count for a moment</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">On handsome amends at the hands of the murderer;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Grendel is unremitting in his persecutions.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The monster of evil fiercely did harass,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The ill-planning death-shade, both elder and younger,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Trapping and tricking them. He trod every night then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The mist-covered moor-fens; men do not know where</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Witches and wizards wander and ramble.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">So the foe of mankind many of evils</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Grievous injuries, often accomplished,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Horrible hermit; Heort he frequented,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gem-bedecked palace, when night-shades had fallen</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">God is against the monster.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">(Since God did oppose him, not the throne could he touch,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001052\">5</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The light-flashing jewel, love of Him knew not).</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Twas a fearful affliction to the friend of the Scyldings</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The king and his council deliberate in vain.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Soul-crushing sorrow. Not seldom in private</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sat the king in his council; conference held they</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">What the braves should determine ’gainst terrors unlooked for.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">They invoke the aid of their gods.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">At the shrines of their idols often they promised</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gifts and offerings, earnestly prayed they</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The devil from hell would help them to lighten</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Their people’s oppression. Such practice they used then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hope of the heathen; hell they remembered</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In innermost spirit, God they knew not,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The true God they do not know.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Judge of their actions, All-wielding Ruler,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">No praise could they give the Guardian of Heaven,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The Wielder of Glory. Woe will be his who</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Through furious hatred his spirit shall drive to</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">70</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The clutch of the fire, no comfort shall look for,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wax no wiser; well for the man who,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Living his life-days, his Lord may face</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And find defence in his Father’s embrace!</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000905\">[1]</$link> The translation is based on ‘<span class=\"ang\">weras</span>,’ adopted by H.-So.—K. and Th. read ‘<span class=\"ang\">wera</span>’ and, arranging differently, render 119(2)-120: <i>They knew not sorrow, the wretchedness of man, aught of misfortune</i>.—For ‘<span class=\"ang\">unhælo</span>’ (120) R. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">unfælo</span>’: <i>The uncanny creature, greedy and cruel, etc</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000955\">[2]</$link> S. rearranges and translates: <i>So he ruled and struggled unjustly, one against all, till the noblest of buildings stood useless (it was a long while) twelve years’ time: the friend of the Scyldings suffered distress, every woe, great sorrows, etc</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000965\">[3]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">syððan</span>,’ B. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">sárcwidum</span>’: <i>Hence in mournful words it became well known, etc</i>. Various other words beginning with ‘s’ have been conjectured.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000977\">[4]</$link> The H.-So. glossary is very inconsistent in referring to this passage.—‘<span class=\"ang\">Sibbe</span>’ (154), which H.-So. regards as an instr., B. takes as accus., obj. of ‘<span class=\"ang\">wolde</span>.’ Putting a comma after <span class=\"ang\">Deniga</span>, he renders: <i>He did not desire peace with any of the Danes, nor did he wish to remove their life-woe, nor to settle for money</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001003\">[5]</$link> Of this difficult passage the following interpretations among others are given: (1) Though Grendel has frequented Heorot as a demon, he could not become ruler of the Danes, on account of his hostility to God. (2) Hrothgar was much grieved that Grendel had not appeared before his throne to receive presents. (3) He was not permitted to devastate the hall, on account of the Creator; <i>i.e.</i> God wished to make his visit fatal to him.—<span class=\"ang\">Ne … wisse</span> (169) W. renders: <i>Nor had he any desire to do so</i>; ‘his’ being obj. gen. = <span class=\"ang\">danach</span>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2 class=\"num\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000053\">IV.</$link></h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>BEOWULF GOES TO HROTHGAR’S ASSISTANCE.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Hrothgar sees no way of escape from the persecutions of Grendel.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">So Healfdene’s kinsman constantly mused on</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His long-lasting sorrow; the battle-thane clever</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Was not anywise able evils to ’scape from:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Too crushing the sorrow that came to the people,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Loathsome and lasting the life-grinding torture,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf, the Geat, hero of the poem, hears of Hrothgar’s sorrow, and resolves to go to his assistance.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Greatest of night-woes. So Higelac’s liegeman,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Good amid Geatmen, of Grendel’s achievements</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Heard in his home:<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001200\">1</$link></sup> of heroes then living</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He was stoutest and strongest, sturdy and noble.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He bade them prepare him a bark that was trusty;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He said he the war-king would seek o’er the ocean,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The folk-leader noble, since he needed retainers.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For the perilous project prudent companions</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Chided him little, though loving him dearly;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">They egged the brave atheling, augured him glory.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">With fourteen carefully chosen companions, he sets out for Dane-land.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The excellent knight from the folk of the Geatmen</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Had liegemen selected, likest to prove them</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Trustworthy warriors; with fourteen companions</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The vessel he looked for; a liegeman then showed them,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A sea-crafty man, the bounds of the country.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fast the days fleeted; the float was a-water,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The craft by the cliff. Clomb to the prow then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Well-equipped warriors: the wave-currents twisted</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The sea on the sand; soldiers then carried</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">On the breast of the vessel bright-shining jewels,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Handsome war-armor; heroes outshoved then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Warmen the wood-ship, on its wished-for adventure.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"sidenote\">The vessel sails like a bird</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The foamy-necked floater fanned by the breeze,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Likest a bird, glided the waters,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">In twenty four hours they reach the shores of Hrothgar’s dominions</span> <span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Till twenty and four hours thereafter</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The twist-stemmed vessel had traveled such distance</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That the sailing-men saw the sloping embankments,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The sea cliffs gleaming, precipitous mountains,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Nesses enormous<span class=\"add\">:</span> they were nearing the limits</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">At the end of the ocean.<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001202\">2</$link></sup> Up thence quickly</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The men of the Weders clomb to the mainland,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fastened their vessel (battle weeds rattled,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">War burnies clattered), the Wielder they thanked</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That the ways o’er the waters had waxen so gentle.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">They are hailed by the Danish coast guard</span> <span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then well from the cliff edge the guard of the Scyldings</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who the sea-cliffs should see to, saw o’er the gangway</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Brave ones bearing beauteous targets,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Armor all ready, anxiously thought he,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Musing and wondering what men were approaching.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">High on his horse then Hrothgar’s retainer</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Turned him to coastward, mightily brandished</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His lance in his hands, questioned with boldness.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">His challenge</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“Who are ye men here, mail-covered warriors</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Clad in your corslets, come thus a-driving</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A high riding ship o’er the shoals of the waters,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\"><sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001204\">3</$link></sup>And hither ’neath helmets have hied o’er the ocean?</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I have been strand-guard, standing as warden,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Lest enemies ever anywise ravage</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Danish dominions with army of war-ships.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">More boldly never have warriors ventured</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hither to come; of kinsmen’s approval,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Word-leave of warriors, I ween that ye surely</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">He is struck by Beowulf’s appearance.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Nothing have known. Never a greater one</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of earls o’er the earth have <i>I</i> had a sight of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Than is one of your number, a hero in armor;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">No low-ranking fellow<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001206\">4</$link></sup> adorned with his weapons,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">But launching them little, unless looks are deceiving,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And striking appearance. Ere ye pass on your journey</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As treacherous spies to the land of the Scyldings</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And farther fare, I fully must know now</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">What race ye belong to. Ye far-away dwellers,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sea-faring sailors, my simple opinion</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hear ye and hearken: haste is most fitting</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Plainly to tell me what place ye are come from.”</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001075\">[1]</$link> ‘<span class=\"ang\">From hám</span>’ (194) is much disputed. One rendering is: <i>Beowulf, being away from home, heard of Hrothgar’s troubles, etc</i>. Another, that adopted by S. and endorsed in the H.-So. notes, is: <i>B. heard from his neighborhood (neighbors),</i> i.e. <i>in his home, etc</i>. A third is: <i>B., being at home, heard this as occurring away from home</i>. The H.-So. glossary and notes conflict.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001129\">[2]</$link> ‘<span class=\"ang\">Eoletes</span>’ (224) is marked with a (?) by H<span class=\"add\">.</span>-So<span class=\"add\">.;</span> our rendering simply follows his conjecture<span class=\"add\">.</span>—Other conjectures as to ‘<span class=\"ang\">eolet</span>’ are<span class=\"add\">:</span> (1) <i>voyage</i>, (2) <i>toil</i>, <i>labor</i>, (3) <i>hasty journey</i><span class=\"add\">.</span></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001161\">[3]</$link> The lacuna of the MS at this point has been supplied by various conjectures<span class=\"add\">.</span> The reading adopted by H<span class=\"add\">.</span>-So<span class=\"add\">.</span> has been rendered in the above translation<span class=\"add\">.</span> W<span class=\"add\">.</span>, like H<span class=\"add\">.</span>-So<span class=\"add\">.,</span> makes ‘<span class=\"ang\">ic</span>’ the beginning of a new sentence, but, for ‘<span class=\"ang\">helmas bæron</span>,’ he reads ‘<span class=\"ang\">hringed stefnan<span class=\"add\">.’</span></span> This has the advantage of giving a parallel to ‘<span class=\"ang\">brontne ceol</span>’ instead of a kenning for ‘go<span class=\"add\">.</span>’—B puts the (?) after ‘<span class=\"ang\">holmas</span>’, and begins a new sentence at the middle of the line<span class=\"add\">.</span> Translate<span class=\"add\">:</span> <i>What warriors are ye, clad in armor, who have thus come bringing the foaming vessel over the water way, hither over the seas? For some time on the wall I have been coast guard, etc</i>. S<span class=\"add\">.</span> endorses most of what B<span class=\"add\">.</span> says, but leaves out ‘on the wall’ in the last sentence. If W.’s ‘<span class=\"ang\">hringed stefnan</span>’ be accepted, change <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001161\">line 51</$link> above to, <i>A ring-stemmed vessel hither o’ersea</i><span class=\"add\">.</span></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001181\">[4]</$link> ‘<span class=\"ang\">Seld-guma</span>’ (249) is variously rendered: (1) <i>housecarle</i>; (2) <i>home-stayer</i>; (3) <i>common man</i>. Dr. H. Wood suggests <i>a man-at-arms in another’s house</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
