        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2 class=\"num\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000059\">VII.</$link></h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>HROTHGAR AND BEOWULF.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Hrothgar remembers Beowulf as a youth, and also remembers his father.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hrothgar answered, helm of the Scyldings:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“I remember this man as the merest of striplings.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His father long dead now was Ecgtheow titled,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Him Hrethel the Geatman granted at home his</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">One only daughter; his battle-brave son</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Is come but now, sought a trustworthy friend.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Seafaring sailors asserted it then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf is reported to have the strength of thirty men.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who valuable gift-gems of the Geatmen<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001631\">1</$link></sup> carried</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As peace-offering thither, that he thirty men’s grapple</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Has in his hand, the hero-in-battle.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">God hath sent him to our rescue.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The holy Creator usward sent him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To West-Dane warriors, I ween, for to render</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Gainst Grendel’s grimness gracious assistance:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I shall give to the good one gift-gems for courage.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hasten to bid them hither to speed them,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001633\">2</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To see assembled this circle of kinsmen;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Tell them expressly they’re welcome in sooth to</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The men of the Danes.” To the door of the building</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"sidenote\">Wulfgar invites the strangers in.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wulfgar went then, this word-message shouted:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“My victorious liegelord bade me to tell you,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The East-Danes’ atheling, that your origin knows he,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And o’er wave-billows wafted ye welcome are hither,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Valiant of spirit. Ye straightway may enter</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Clad in corslets, cased in your helmets,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To see King Hrothgar. Here let your battle-boards,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wood-spears and war-shafts, await your conferring.”</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The mighty one rose then, with many a liegeman,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">An excellent thane-group; some there did await them,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And as bid of the brave one the battle-gear guarded.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Together they hied them, while the hero did guide them,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Neath Heorot’s roof; the high-minded went then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sturdy ’neath helmet till he stood in the building.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Beowulf spake (his burnie did glisten,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His armor seamed over by the art of the craftsman):</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf salutes Hrothgar, and then proceeds to boast of his youthful achievements.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“Hail thou, Hrothgar! I am Higelac’s kinsman</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And vassal forsooth; many a wonder</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I dared as a stripling. The doings of Grendel,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In far-off fatherland I fully did know of:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sea-farers tell us, this hall-building standeth,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Excellent edifice, empty and useless</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To all the earlmen after evenlight’s glimmer</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Neath heaven’s bright hues hath hidden its glory.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">This my earls then urged me, the most excellent of them,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Carles very clever, to come and assist thee,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Folk-leader Hrothgar; fully they knew of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">His fight with the nickers.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The strength of my body. Themselves they beheld me</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When I came from the contest, when covered with gore</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Foes I escaped from, where five<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001635\">3</$link></sup> I had bound,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The giant-race wasted, in the waters destroying</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The nickers by night, bore numberless sorrows,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The Weders avenged (woes had they suffered)</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Enemies ravaged; alone now with Grendel</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">He intends to fight Grendel unaided.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I shall manage the matter, with the monster of evil,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The giant, decide it. Thee I would therefore</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Beg of thy bounty, Bright-Danish chieftain,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Lord of the Scyldings, this single petition:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Not to refuse me, defender of warriors,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Friend-lord of folks, so far have I sought thee,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That <i>I</i> may unaided, my earlmen assisting me,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">This brave-mooded war-band, purify Heorot.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I have heard on inquiry, the horrible creature</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Since the monster uses no weapons,</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">From veriest rashness recks not for weapons;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I this do scorn then, so be Higelac gracious,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">My liegelord belovèd, lenient of spirit,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To bear a blade or a broad-fashioned target,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A shield to the onset; only with hand-grip</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">I, too, shall disdain to use any.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The foe I must grapple, fight for my life then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Foeman with foeman; he fain must rely on</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The doom of the Lord whom death layeth hold of.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Should he crush me, he will eat my companions as he has eaten thy thanes.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">70</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I ween he will wish, if he win in the struggle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To eat in the war-hall earls of the Geat-folk,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Boldly to swallow<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001637\">4</$link></sup> them, as of yore he did often</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The best of the Hrethmen! Thou needest not trouble</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A head-watch to give me;<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001639\">5</$link></sup> he will have me dripping</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"sidenote\">In case of my defeat, thou wilt not have the trouble of burying me.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">75</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And dreary with gore, if death overtake me,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001641\">6</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Will bear me off bleeding, biting and mouthing me,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The hermit will eat me, heedless of pity,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Marking the moor-fens; no more wilt thou need then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Should I fall, send my armor to my lord, King Higelac.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Find me my food.<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001643\">7</$link></sup> If I fall in the battle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">80</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Send to Higelac the armor that serveth</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To shield my bosom, the best of equipments,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Richest of ring-mails; ’tis the relic of Hrethla,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Weird is supreme</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The work of Wayland. Goes Weird as she must go!”</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001478\">[1]</$link> Some render ‘<span class=\"ang\">gif-sceattas</span>’ by ‘tribute.’—‘<span class=\"ang\">Géata</span>’ B. and Th. emended to ‘<span class=\"ang\">Géatum</span>.’ If this be accepted, change ‘<i>of</i> the Geatmen’ to ‘<i>to</i> the Geatmen.’</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001492\">[2]</$link> If t.B.’s emendation of vv. 386, 387 be accepted, the two lines, ‘Hasten … kinsmen’ will read: <i>Hasten thou, bid the throng of kinsmen go into the hall together</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001558\">[3]</$link> For 420 (<i>b</i>) and 421 (<i>a</i>), B. suggests: <span class=\"ang\">Þær ic (on) fífelgeban ýðde eotena cyn</span> = <i>where I in the ocean destroyed the eoten-race</i>.—t.B. accepts B.’s “brilliant” ‘<span class=\"ang\">fífelgeban</span>,’ omits ‘<span class=\"ang\">on</span>,’ emends ‘<span class=\"ang\">cyn</span>’ to ‘<span class=\"ang\">hám</span>,’ arranging: <span class=\"ang\">Þær ic fífelgeban ýðde, eotena hám</span> = <i>where I desolated the ocean, the home of the eotens</i>.—This would be better but for changing ‘<span class=\"ang\">cyn</span>’ to ‘<span class=\"ang\">hám</span>.’—I suggest: <span class=\"ang\">Þær ic fífelgeband (cf. nhd. Bande) ýðde, eotena cyn</span> = <i>where I conquered the monster band, the race of the eotens</i>. This makes no change except to read ‘<i>fífel</i>’ for ‘<i>fífe</i>.’</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001606\">[4]</$link> ‘<span class=\"ang\">Unforhte</span>’ (444) is much disputed.—H.-So. wavers between adj. and adv. Gr. and B. take it as an adv. modifying <i><span class=\"ang\">etan</span>: Will eat the Geats fearlessly</i>.—Kl. considers this reading absurd, and proposes ‘<span class=\"ang\">anforhte</span>’ = timid.—Understanding ‘<span class=\"ang\">unforhte</span>’ as an adj. has this advantage, viz. that it gives a parallel to ‘<span class=\"ang\">Geátena leóde</span>’: but to take it as an adv. is more natural. Furthermore, to call the Geats ‘brave’ might, at this point, seem like an implied thrust at the Danes, so long helpless; while to call his own men ‘timid’ would be befouling his own nest.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001610\">[5]</$link> For ‘head-watch,’ cf. H.-So. notes and cf. v. 2910.—Th. translates: <i>Thou wilt not need my head to hide</i> (i.e., thou wilt have no occasion to bury me, as Grendel will devour me whole).—Simrock imagines a kind of dead-watch.—Dr. H. Wood suggests: <i>Thou wilt not have to bury so much as my head</i> (for Grendel will be a thorough undertaker),—grim humor.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001612\">[6]</$link> S. proposes a colon after ‘<span class=\"ang\">nimeð</span>’ (l. 447). This would make no essential change in the translation.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001620\">[7]</$link> Owing to the vagueness of ‘<span class=\"ang\">feorme</span>’ (451), this passage is variously translated. In our translation, H.-So.’s glossary has been quite closely followed. This agrees substantially with B.’s translation (P. and B. XII. 87). R. translates: <i>Thou needst not take care longer as to the consumption of my dead body.</i> ‘<span class=\"ang\">Líc</span>’ is also a crux here, as it may mean living body or dead body.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000001647": {
            "role": "text",
