        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>BEOWULF RECEIVES FURTHER HONOR.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">More gifts are offered Beowulf.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A beaker was borne him, and bidding to quaff it</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Graciously given, and gold that was twisted</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Pleasantly proffered, a pair of arm-jewels,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Rings and corslet, of collars the greatest</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I’ve heard of ’neath heaven. Of heroes not any</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">More splendid from jewels have I heard ’neath the welkin,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">A famous necklace is referred to, in comparison with the gems presented to Beowulf.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Since Hama off bore the Brosingmen’s necklace,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The bracteates and jewels, from the bright-shining city,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003371\">1</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Eormenric’s cunning craftiness fled from,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Chose gain everlasting. Geatish Higelac,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Grandson of Swerting, last had this jewel</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When tramping ’neath banner the treasure he guarded,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The field-spoil defended; Fate offcarried him</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When for deeds of daring he endured tribulation,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hate from the Frisians; the ornaments bare he</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">O’er the cup of the currents, costly gem-treasures,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Mighty folk-leader, he fell ’neath his target;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003373\">2</$link></sup> corpse of the king then came into charge of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The race of the Frankmen, the mail-shirt and collar:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Warmen less noble plundered the fallen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When the fight was finished; the folk of the Geatmen</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The field of the dead held in possession.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The choicest of mead-halls with cheering resounded.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wealhtheo discoursed, the war-troop addressed she:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Queen Wealhtheow magnifies Beowulf’s achievements.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“This collar enjoy thou, Beowulf worthy,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Young man, in safety, and use thou this armor,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gems of the people, and prosper thou fully,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Show thyself sturdy and be to these liegemen</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Mild with instruction! I’ll mind thy requital.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Thou hast brought it to pass that far and near</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Forever and ever earthmen shall honor thee,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Even so widely as ocean surroundeth</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The blustering bluffs. Be, while thou livest,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A wealth-blessèd atheling. I wish thee most truly</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">May gifts never fail thee.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Jewels and treasure. Be kind to my son, thou</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Living in joyance! Here each of the nobles</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Is true unto other, gentle in spirit,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Loyal to leader. The liegemen are peaceful,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The war-troops ready: well-drunken heroes,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003375\">3</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Do as I bid ye.” Then she went to the settle.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">There was choicest of banquets, wine drank the heroes:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">They little know of the sorrow in store for them.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Weird they knew not, destiny cruel,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As to many an earlman early it happened,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When evening had come and Hrothgar had parted</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Off to his manor, the mighty to slumber.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Warriors unnumbered warded the building</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As erst they did often: the ale-settle bared they,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Twas covered all over with beds and pillows.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">A doomed thane is there with them.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Doomed unto death, down to his slumber</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bowed then a beer-thane. Their battle-shields placed they,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bright-shining targets, up by their heads then;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">O’er the atheling on ale-bench ’twas easy to see there</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Battle-high helmet, burnie of ring-mail,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">They were always ready for battle.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And mighty war-spear. ’Twas the wont of that people</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To constantly keep them equipped for the battle,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003377\">4</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">At home or marching—in either condition—</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">At seasons just such as necessity ordered</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As best for their ruler; that people was worthy.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003268\">[1]</$link> C. suggests a semicolon after ‘city,’ with ‘he’ as supplied subject of ‘fled’ and ‘chose.’</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003288\">[2]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">feorh</span>’ S. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">feoh</span>’: ‘corpse’ in the translation would then be changed to ‘<i>possessions</i>,’ ‘<i>belongings</i>.’ This is a better reading than one joining, in such intimate syntactical relations, things so unlike as ‘corpse’ and ‘jewels.’</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003330\">[3]</$link> S. suggests ‘<i>wine-joyous heroes</i>,’ ‘<i>warriors elated with wine</i>.’</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003362\">[4]</$link> I believe this translation brings out the meaning of the poet, without departing seriously from the H.-So. text. ‘Oft’ frequently means ‘constantly,’ ‘continually,’ not always ‘often.’—Why ‘<span class=\"ang\">an (on) wíg gearwe</span>’ should be written ‘<span class=\"ang\">ánwíg-gearwe</span>’ (= ready for single combat), I cannot see. ‘<span class=\"ang\">Gearwe</span>’ occurs quite frequently with ‘<span class=\"ang\">on</span>’; cf. B. 1110 (<i>ready for the pyre</i>), El. 222 (<i>ready for the glad journey</i>). Moreover, what has the idea of single combat to do with B. 1247 ff.? The poet is giving an inventory of the arms and armor which they lay aside on retiring, and he closes his narration by saying that they were <i>always prepared for battle both at home and on the march</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2 class=\"num\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000091\">XX.</$link></h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>THE MOTHER OF GRENDEL.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">They sank then to slumber. With sorrow one paid for</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His evening repose, as often betid them</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">While Grendel was holding<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003527\">1</$link></sup> the gold-bedecked palace,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Ill-deeds performing, till his end overtook him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Death for his sins. ’Twas seen very clearly,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Grendel’s mother is known to be thirsting for revenge.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Known unto earth-folk, that still an avenger</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Outlived the loathed one, long since the sorrow</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Caused by the struggle; the mother of Grendel,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Devil-shaped woman, her woe ever minded,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who was held to inhabit the horrible waters,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">[Grendel’s progenitor, Cain, is again referred to.]</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The cold-flowing currents, after Cain had become a</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Slayer-with-edges to his one only brother,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The son of his sire; he set out then banished,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Marked as a murderer, man-joys avoiding,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Lived in the desert. Thence demons unnumbered</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The poet again magnifies Beowulf’s valor.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fate-sent awoke; one of them Grendel,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sword-cursèd, hateful, who at Heorot met with</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A man that was watching, waiting the struggle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Where a horrid one held him with hand-grapple sturdy;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Nathless he minded the might of his body,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The glorious gift God had allowed him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And folk-ruling Father’s favor relied on,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His help and His comfort: so he conquered the foeman,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The hell-spirit humbled: he unhappy departed then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Reaved of his joyance, journeying to death-haunts,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Foeman of man. His mother moreover</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Grendel’s mother comes to avenge her son.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Eager and gloomy was anxious to go on</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Her mournful mission, mindful of vengeance</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For the death of her son. She came then to Heorot</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Where the Armor-Dane earlmen all through the building</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Were lying in slumber. Soon there became then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Return<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003529\">2</$link></sup> to the nobles, when the mother of Grendel</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Entered the folk-hall; the fear was less grievous</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">By even so much as the vigor of maidens,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">War-strength of women, by warrior is reckoned,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When well-carved weapon, worked with the hammer,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Blade very bloody, brave with its edges,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Strikes down the boar-sign that stands on the helmet.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then the hard-edgèd weapon was heaved in the building,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003531\">3</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The brand o’er the benches, broad-lindens many</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hand-fast were lifted; for helmet he recked not,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For armor-net broad, whom terror laid hold of.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">She went then hastily, outward would get her</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Her life for to save, when some one did spy her;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">She seizes a favorite liegemen of Hrothgar’s.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Soon she had grappled one of the athelings</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fast and firmly, when fenward she hied her;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That one to Hrothgar was liefest of heroes</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In rank of retainer where waters encircle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A mighty shield-warrior, whom she murdered at slumber,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A broadly-famed battle-knight. Beowulf was absent,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf was asleep in another part of the palace.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">But another apartment was erstwhile devoted</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To the glory-decked Geatman when gold was distributed.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">There was hubbub in Heorot. The hand that was famous</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">She grasped in its gore;<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003533\">4</$link></sup> grief was renewed then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In homes and houses: ’twas no happy arrangement</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In both of the quarters to barter and purchase</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With lives of their friends. Then the well-agèd ruler,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The gray-headed war-thane, was woful in spirit,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When his long-trusted liegeman lifeless he knew of,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf is sent for.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His dearest one gone. Quick from a room was</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Beowulf brought, brave and triumphant.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As day was dawning in the dusk of the morning,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">He comes at Hrothgar’s summons.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Went then that earlman, champion noble,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Came with comrades, where the clever one bided</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Whether God all gracious would grant him a respite</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">After the woe he had suffered. The war-worthy hero</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With a troop of retainers trod then the pavement</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">(The hall-building groaned), till he greeted the wise one,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf inquires how Hrothgar had enjoyed his night’s rest.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The earl of the Ingwins;<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003535\">5</$link></sup> asked if the night had</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">70</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fully refreshed him, as fain he would have it.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003390\">[1]</$link> Several eminent authorities either read or emend the MS. so as to make this verse read, <i>While Grendel was wasting the gold-bedecked palace</i>. So <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003414\">20 <span class=\"smaller\">15</span></$link> below: <i>ravaged the desert</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003448\">[2]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">sóna</span>’ (1281), t.B. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">sára</span>,’ limiting ‘<span class=\"ang\">edhwyrft</span>.’ Read then: <i>Return of sorrows to the nobles, etc</i>. This emendation supplies the syntactical gap after ‘<span class=\"ang\">edhwyrft</span>.’</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003462\">[3]</$link> Some authorities follow Grein’s lexicon in treating ‘<span class=\"ang\">heard ecg</span>’ as an adj. limiting ‘<span class=\"ang\">sweord</span>’: H.-So. renders it as a subst. (So v. 1491.) The sense of the translation would be the same.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003492\">[4]</$link> B. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">under hróf genam</span>’ (v. 1303). This emendation, as well as an emendation with (?) to v. 739, he offers, because ‘<span class=\"ang\">under</span>’ baffles him in both passages. All we need is to take ‘<span class=\"ang\">under</span>’ in its secondary meaning of ‘in,’ which, though not given by Grein, occurs in the literature. Cf. Chron. 876 (March’s A.-S. Gram. § 355) and Oro. Amaz. I. 10, where ‘<span class=\"ang\">under</span>’ = <i>in the midst of</i>. Cf. modern Eng. ‘in such circumstances,’ which interchanges in good usage with ‘under such circumstances.’</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003522\">[5]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">néod-laðu</span>’ (1321) C. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">néad-láðum</span>,’ and translates: <i>asked whether the night had been pleasant to him after crushing-hostility</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
