        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003984\">[2]</$link> Sw., R., and t.B. suggest ‘<span class=\"ang\">feaxe</span>’ for ‘<span class=\"ang\">eaxle</span>’ (1538) and render: <i>Seized by the hair</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000003992\">[3]</$link> If ‘<span class=\"ang\">hand-léan</span>’ be accepted (as the MS. has it), the line will read: <i>She hand-reward gave him early thereafter</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004020\">[4]</$link> Sw. and S. change H.-So.’s semicolon (v<span class=\"add\">.</span> 1557) to a comma, and translate: <i>The Ruler of Heaven arranged it in justice easily, after he arose again</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004032",
