        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2 class=\"num\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000099\">XXIV.</$link></h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>BEOWULF IS DOUBLE-CONQUEROR.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf grasps a giant-sword,</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then he saw mid the war-gems a weapon of victory,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">An ancient giant-sword, of edges a-doughty,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Glory of warriors: of weapons ’twas choicest,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Only ’twas larger than any man else was</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Able to bear to the battle-encounter,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The good and splendid work of the giants.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He grasped then the sword-hilt, knight of the Scyldings,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bold and battle-grim, brandished his ring-sword,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hopeless of living, hotly he smote her,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That the fiend-woman’s neck firmly it grappled,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">and fells the female monster.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Broke through her bone-joints, the bill fully pierced her</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fate-cursèd body, she fell to the ground then:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The hand-sword was bloody, the hero exulted.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The brand was brilliant, brightly it glimmered,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Just as from heaven gemlike shineth</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The torch of the firmament. He glanced ’long the building,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And turned by the wall then, Higelac’s vassal</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Raging and wrathful raised his battle-sword</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Strong by the handle. The edge was not useless</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To the hero-in-battle, but he speedily wished to</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Give Grendel requital for the many assaults he</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Had worked on the West-Danes not once, but often,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When he slew in slumber the subjects of Hrothgar,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Swallowed down fifteen sleeping retainers</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of the folk of the Danemen, and fully as many</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Carried away, a horrible prey.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He gave him requital, grim-raging champion,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf sees the body of Grendel, and cuts off his head.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When he saw on his rest-place weary of conflict</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Grendel lying, of life-joys bereavèd,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As the battle at Heorot erstwhile had scathed him;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His body far bounded, a blow when he suffered,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Death having seized him, sword-smiting heavy,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And he cut off his head then. Early this noticed</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The clever carles who as comrades of Hrothgar</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The waters are gory.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gazed on the sea-deeps, that the surging wave-currents</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Were mightily mingled, the mere-flood was gory:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of the good one the gray-haired together held converse,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf is given up for dead.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The hoary of head, that they hoped not to see again</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The atheling ever, that exulting in victory</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He’d return there to visit the distinguished folk-ruler:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then many concluded the mere-wolf had killed him.<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004221\">1</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The ninth hour came then. From the ness-edge departed</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The bold-mooded Scyldings; the gold-friend of heroes</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Homeward betook him. The strangers sat down then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Soul-sick, sorrowful, the sea-waves regarding:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">They wished and yet weened not their well-loved friend-lord</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The giant-sword melts.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To see any more. The sword-blade began then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The blood having touched it, contracting and shriveling</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With battle-icicles; ’twas a wonderful marvel</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That it melted entirely, likest to ice when</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The Father unbindeth the bond of the frost and</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Unwindeth the wave-bands, He who wieldeth dominion</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of times and of tides: a truth-firm Creator.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Nor took he of jewels more in the dwelling,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Lord of the Weders, though they lay all around him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Than the head and the handle handsome with jewels;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The brand early melted, burnt was the weapon:<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004233\">2</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">So hot was the blood, the strange-spirit poisonous</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The hero swims back to the realms of day.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That in it did perish. He early swam off then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who had bided in combat the carnage of haters,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Went up through the ocean; the eddies were cleansèd,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The spacious expanses, when the spirit from farland</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His life put aside and this short-lived existence.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The seamen’s defender came swimming to land then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Doughty of spirit, rejoiced in his sea-gift,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The bulky burden which he bore in his keeping.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The excellent vassals advanced then to meet him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To God they were grateful, were glad in their chieftain,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That to see him safe and sound was granted them.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">70</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">From the high-minded hero, then, helmet and burnie</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Were speedily loosened: the ocean was putrid,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The water ’neath welkin weltered with gore.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Forth did they fare, then, their footsteps retracing,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Merry and mirthful, measured the earth-way,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">75</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The highway familiar: men very daring<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004235\">3</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bare then the head from the sea-cliff, burdening</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Each of the earlmen, excellent-valiant.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">It takes four men to carry Grendel’s head on a spear.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Four of them had to carry with labor</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The head of Grendel to the high towering gold-hall</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">80</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Upstuck on the spear, till fourteen most-valiant</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And battle-brave Geatmen came there going</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Straight to the palace: the prince of the people</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Measured the mead-ways, their mood-brave companion.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The atheling of earlmen entered the building,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">85</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Deed-valiant man, adorned with distinction,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Doughty shield-warrior, to address King Hrothgar:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then hung by the hair, the head of Grendel</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Was borne to the building, where beer-thanes were drinking,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Loth before earlmen and eke ’fore the lady:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">90</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The warriors beheld then a wonderful sight.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004120\">[1]</$link> ‘<span class=\"ang\">Þæs monige gewearð</span>’ (1599) and ‘<span class=\"ang\">hafað þæs geworden</span>’ (2027).—In a paper published some years ago in one of the Johns Hopkins University circulars, I tried to throw upon these two long-doubtful passages some light derived from a study of like passages in Alfred’s prose.—The impersonal verb ‘<span class=\"ang\">geweorðan</span>,’ with an accus. of the person, and a <span class=\"ang\">þæt</span>-clause is used several times with the meaning ‘agree.’ See Orosius (Sweet’s ed.) 178<sub>7</sub>; 204<sub>34</sub>; 208<sub>28</sub>; 210<sub>15</sub>; 280<sub>20</sub>. In the two Beowulf passages, the <span class=\"ang\">þæt</span>-clause is anticipated by ‘<span class=\"ang\">þæs</span>,’ which is clearly a gen. of the thing agreed on.\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p>The first passage (v. 1599 (b)-1600) I translate literally: <i>Then many agreed upon this (namely), that the sea-wolf had killed him</i>.</p></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p>The second passage (v. 2025 (b)-2027): <i>She is promised …; to this the friend of the Scyldings has agreed, etc</i>. By emending ‘<span class=\"ang\">is</span>’ instead of ‘<span class=\"ang\">wæs</span>’ (2025), the tenses will be brought into perfect harmony.</p></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p>In v. 1997 ff. this same idiom occurs, and was noticed in B.’s great article on Beowulf, which appeared about the time I published my reading of 1599 and 2027. Translate 1997 then: <i>Wouldst let the South-Danes themselves decide about their struggle with Grendel</i>. Here ‘<span class=\"ang\">Súð-Dene</span>’ is accus. of person, and ‘<span class=\"ang\">gúðe</span>’ is gen. of thing agreed on.</p></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p>With such collateral support as that afforded by B. (P. and B. XII. 97), I have no hesitation in departing from H.-So., my usual guide.</p></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p>The idiom above treated runs through A.-S., Old Saxon, and other Teutonic languages, and should be noticed in the lexicons.</p></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004152\">[2]</$link> ‘<span class=\"ang\">Bróden-mæl</span>’ is regarded by most scholars as meaning a damaskeened sword. Translate: <i>The damaskeened sword burned up</i>. Cf. <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004275\">25 <span class=\"smaller\">16</span></$link> and note.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004188\">[3]</$link> ‘<span class=\"ang\">Cyning-balde</span>’ (1635) is the much-disputed reading of K. and Th. To render this, “<i>nobly bold</i>,” “<i>excellently bold</i>,” have been suggested. B. would read ‘<span class=\"ang\">cyning-holde</span>’ (cf. 290), and render: <i>Men well-disposed towards the king carried the head, etc.</i> ‘<span class=\"ang\">Cynebealde</span>,’ says t.B., endorsing Gr.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
