        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf’s farewell.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Beowulf spake, Ecgtheow’s offspring:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“We men of the water wish to declare now</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fared from far-lands, we’re firmly determined</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To seek King Higelac. Here have we fitly</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Been welcomed and feasted, as heart would desire it;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Good was the greeting. If greater affection</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I am anywise able ever on earth to</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gain at thy hands, ruler of heroes,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Than yet I have done, I shall quickly be ready</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">I shall be ever ready to aid thee.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For combat and conflict. O’er the course of the waters</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Learn I that neighbors alarm thee with terror,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As haters did whilom, I hither will bring thee</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For help unto heroes henchmen by thousands.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">My liegelord will encourage me in aiding thee.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I know as to Higelac, the lord of the Geatmen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Though young in years, he yet will permit me,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">By words and by works, ward of the people,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fully to furnish thee forces and bear thee</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">My lance to relieve thee, if liegemen shall fail thee,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And help of my hand-strength; if Hrethric be treating,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bairn of the king, at the court of the Geatmen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He thereat may find him friends in abundance:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Faraway countries he were better to seek for</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who trusts in himself.” Hrothgar discoursed then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Making rejoinder: “These words thou hast uttered</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">All-knowing God hath given thy spirit!</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">O Beowulf, thou art wise beyond thy years.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Ne’er heard I an earlman thus early in life</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">More clever in speaking: thou’rt cautious of spirit,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Mighty of muscle, in mouth-answers prudent.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I count on the hope that, happen it ever</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That missile shall rob thee of Hrethel’s descendant,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Edge-horrid battle, and illness or weapon</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Deprive thee of prince, of people’s protector,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Should Higelac die, the Geats could find no better successor than thou wouldst make.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And life thou yet holdest, the Sea-Geats will never</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Find a more fitting folk-lord to choose them,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gem-ward of heroes, than <i>thou</i> mightest prove thee,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">If the kingdom of kinsmen thou carest to govern.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Thy mood-spirit likes me the longer the better,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Beowulf dear: thou hast brought it to pass that</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To both these peoples peace shall be common,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Thou hast healed the ancient breach between our races.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To Geat-folk and Danemen, the strife be suspended,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The secret assailings they suffered in yore-days;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And also that jewels be shared while I govern</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The wide-stretching kingdom, and that many shall visit</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Others o’er the ocean with excellent gift-gems:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The ring-adorned bark shall bring o’er the currents</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Presents and love-gifts. This people I know</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Tow’rd foeman and friend firmly established,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004738\">1</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">After ancient etiquette everywise blameless.”</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then the warden of earlmen gave him still farther,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Parting gifts</span> <span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Kinsman of Healfdene, a dozen of jewels,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bade him safely seek with the presents</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His well-beloved people, early returning.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"sidenote\">Hrothgar kisses Beowulf, and weeps.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then the noble-born king kissed the distinguished,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Dear-lovèd liegeman, the Dane-prince saluted him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And claspèd his neck; tears from him fell,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">From the gray-headed man: he two things expected,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Agèd and reverend, but rather the second,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\"><sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004740\">2</$link></sup>That bold in council they’d meet thereafter.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The man was so dear that he failed to suppress the</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Emotions that moved him, but in mood-fetters fastened</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The old king is deeply grieved to part with his benefactor.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The long-famous hero longeth in secret</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Deep in his spirit for the dear-beloved man</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Though not a blood-kinsman. Beowulf thenceward,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gold-splendid warrior, walked o’er the meadows</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Exulting in treasure: the sea-going vessel</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Riding at anchor awaited its owner.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As they pressed on their way then, the present of Hrothgar</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Giving liberally is the true proof of kingship.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Was frequently referred to: a folk-king indeed that</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Everyway blameless, till age did debar him</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">70</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The joys of his might, which hath many oft injured.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004689\">[1]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">geworhte</span>,’ the crux of this passage, B. proposes ‘<span class=\"ang\">geþóhte</span>,’ rendering: <i>I know this people with firm thought every way blameless towards foe and friends</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004711\">[2]</$link> S. and B. emend so as to negative the verb ‘meet.’ “Why should Hrothgar weep if he expects to meet Beowulf again?” both these scholars ask. But the weeping is mentioned before the ‘expectations’: the tears may have been due to many emotions, especially gratitude, struggling for expression.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004741": {
