        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2 class=\"num\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000111\">XXVIII.</$link></h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>THE HOMEWARD JOURNEY.—THE TWO QUEENS.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then the band of very valiant retainers</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Came to the current; they were clad all in armor,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The coast-guard again.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In link-woven burnies. The land-warder noticed</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The return of the earlmen, as he erstwhile had seen them;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Nowise with insult he greeted the strangers</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">From the naze of the cliff, but rode on to meet them;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Said the bright-armored visitors<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004892\">1</$link></sup> vesselward traveled</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Welcome to Weders. The wide-bosomed craft then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Lay on the sand, laden with armor,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With horses and jewels, the ring-stemmèd sailer:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The mast uptowered o’er the treasure of Hrothgar.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf gives the guard a handsome sword.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To the boat-ward a gold-bound brand he presented,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That he was afterwards honored on the ale-bench more highly</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As the heirloom’s owner. <sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004894\">2</$link></sup>Set he out on his vessel,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To drive on the deep, Dane-country left he.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Along by the mast then a sea-garment fluttered,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A rope-fastened sail. The sea-boat resounded,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The wind o’er the waters the wave-floater nowise</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Kept from its journey; the sea-goer traveled,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The foamy-necked floated forth o’er the currents,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The well-fashioned vessel o’er the ways of the ocean,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The Geats see their own land again.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Till they came within sight of the cliffs of the Geatmen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The well-known headlands. The wave-goer hastened</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Driven by breezes, stood on the shore.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The port-warden is anxiously looking for them.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Prompt at the ocean, the port-ward was ready,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who long in the past outlooked in the distance,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004896\">3</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">At water’s-edge waiting well-lovèd heroes;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He bound to the bank then the broad-bosomed vessel</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fast in its fetters, lest the force of the waters</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Should be able to injure the ocean-wood winsome.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bade he up then take the treasure of princes,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Plate-gold and fretwork; not far was it thence</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To go off in search of the giver of jewels:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hrethel’s son Higelac at home there remaineth,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004898\">4</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Himself with his comrades close to the sea-coast.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The building was splendid, the king heroic,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Great in his hall, Hygd very young was,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Hygd, the noble queen of Higelac, lavish of gifts.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fine-mooded, clever, though few were the winters</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That the daughter of Hæreth had dwelt in the borough;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">But she nowise was cringing nor niggard of presents,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of ornaments rare, to the race of the Geatmen.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Offa’s consort, Thrytho, is contrasted with Hygd.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Thrytho nursed anger, excellent<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004900\">5</$link></sup> folk-queen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hot-burning hatred: no hero whatever</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Mong household companions, her husband excepted</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">She is a terror to all save her husband.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Dared to adventure to look at the woman</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With eyes in the daytime;<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004902\">6</$link></sup> but he knew that death-chains</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hand-wreathed were wrought him: early thereafter,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When the hand-strife was over, edges were ready,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That fierce-raging sword-point had to force a decision,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Murder-bale show. Such no womanly custom</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For a lady to practise, though lovely her person,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That a weaver-of-peace, on pretence of anger</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A belovèd liegeman of life should deprive.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Soothly this hindered Heming’s kinsman;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Other ale-drinking earlmen asserted</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That fearful folk-sorrows fewer she wrought them,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Treacherous doings, since first she was given</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Adorned with gold to the war-hero youthful,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For her origin honored, when Offa’s great palace</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">O’er the fallow flood by her father’s instructions</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">She sought on her journey, where she afterwards fully,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Famed for her virtue, her fate on the king’s-seat</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Enjoyed in her lifetime, love did she hold with</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The ruler of heroes, the best, it is told me,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of all of the earthmen that oceans encompass,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of earl-kindreds endless; hence Offa was famous</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Far and widely, by gifts and by battles,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Spear-valiant hero; the home of his fathers</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He governed with wisdom, whence Eomær did issue</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">70</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For help unto heroes, Heming’s kinsman,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Grandson of Garmund, great in encounters.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004761\">[1]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">scawan</span>’ (1896), ‘<span class=\"ang\">scaðan</span>’ has been proposed. Accepting this, we may render: <i>He said the bright-armored warriors were going to their vessel, welcome, etc</i>. (Cf. 1804.)</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004775\">[2]</$link> R. suggests, ‘<span class=\"ang\">Gewát him on naca</span>,’ and renders: <i>The vessel set out, to drive on the sea, the Dane-country left</i>. ‘<span class=\"ang\">On</span>’ bears the alliteration; cf. ‘<span class=\"ang\">on hafu</span>’ (2524). This has some advantages over the H.-So. reading; viz. (1) It adds nothing to the text; (2) it makes ‘<span class=\"ang\">naca</span>’ the subject, and thus brings the passage into keeping with the context, where the poet has exhausted his vocabulary in detailing the actions of the vessel.—B.’s emendation (cf. P. and B. XII. 97) is violent.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004799\">[3]</$link> B. translates: <i>Who for a long time, ready at the coast, had looked out into the distance eagerly for the dear men</i>. This changes the syntax of ‘<span class=\"ang\">léofra manna</span>.’</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004815\">[4]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">wunað</span>’ (v. 1924) several eminent critics suggest ‘<span class=\"ang\">wunade</span>’ (=remained). This makes the passage much clearer.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004831\">[5]</$link> Why should such a woman be described as an ‘excellent’ queen? C. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">frécnu</span>’ = dangerous, bold.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004839\">[6]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">an dæges</span>’ various readings have been offered. If ‘<span class=\"ang\">and-éges</span>’ be accepted, the sentence will read: <i>No hero … dared look upon her, eye to eye</i>. If ‘<span class=\"ang\">án-dæges</span>’ be adopted, translate: <i>Dared look upon her the whole day</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004906": {
