        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The hoard.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He a gem-vessel saw there: many of suchlike</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Ancient ornaments in the earth-cave were lying,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As in days of yore some one of men of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Illustrious lineage, as a legacy monstrous,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">There had secreted them, careful and thoughtful,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Dear-valued jewels. Death had offsnatched them,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In the days of the past, and the one man moreover</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of the flower of the folk who fared there the longest,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Was fain to defer it, friend-mourning warder,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A little longer to be left in enjoyment</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of long-lasting treasure.<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005641\">1</$link></sup> A barrow all-ready</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Stood on the plain the stream-currents nigh to,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">New by the ness-edge, unnethe of approaching:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The keeper of rings carried within a</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\"><sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005643\">2</$link></sup>Ponderous deal of the treasure of nobles,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of gold that was beaten, briefly he spake then:<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005645\">3</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The ring-giver bewails the loss of retainers.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“Hold thou, O Earth, now heroes no more may,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The earnings of earlmen. Lo! erst in thy bosom</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Worthy men won them; war-death hath ravished,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Perilous life-bale, all my warriors,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Liegemen belovèd, who this life have forsaken,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who hall-pleasures saw. No sword-bearer have I,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And no one to burnish the gold-plated vessel,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The high-valued beaker: my heroes are vanished.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The hardy helmet behung with gilding</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Shall be reaved of its riches: the ring-cleansers slumber</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who were charged to have ready visors-for-battle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And the burnie that bided in battle-encounter</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">O’er breaking of war-shields the bite of the edges</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Moulds with the hero. The ring-twisted armor,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Its lord being lifeless, no longer may journey</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hanging by heroes; harp-joy is vanished,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The rapture of glee-wood, no excellent falcon</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Swoops through the building, no swift-footed charger</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Grindeth the gravel. A grievous destruction</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">No few of the world-folk widely hath scattered!”</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">So, woful of spirit one after all</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Lamented mournfully, moaning in sadness</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">By day and by night, till death with its billows</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The fire-dragon</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Dashed on his spirit. Then the ancient dusk-scather</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Found the great treasure standing all open,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He who flaming and fiery flies to the barrows,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Naked war-dragon, nightly escapeth</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Encompassed with fire; men under heaven</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Widely beheld him. ’Tis said that he looks for<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005647\">4</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The hoard in the earth, where old he is guarding</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The heathenish treasure; he’ll be nowise the better.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The dragon meets his match.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">So three-hundred winters the waster of peoples</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Held upon earth that excellent hoard-hall,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Till the forementioned earlman angered him bitterly:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The beat-plated beaker he bare to his chieftain</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And fullest remission for all his remissness</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Begged of his liegelord. Then the hoard<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005649\">5</$link></sup> was discovered,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The treasure was taken, his petition was granted</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The hero plunders the dragon’s den</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The lorn-mooded liegeman. His lord regarded</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The old-work of earth-folk—’twas the earliest occasion.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When the dragon awoke, the strife was renewed there;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He snuffed ’long the stone then, stout-hearted found he</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The footprint of foeman; too far had he gone</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With cunning craftiness close to the head of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">70</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The fire-spewing dragon. So undoomed he may ’scape from</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Anguish and exile with ease who possesseth</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The favor of Heaven. The hoard-warden eagerly</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Searched o’er the ground then, would meet with the person</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That caused him sorrow while in slumber reclining:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">75</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gleaming and wild he oft went round the cavern,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">All of it outward; not any of earthmen</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Was seen in that desert.<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005651\">6</$link></sup> Yet he joyed in the battle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Rejoiced in the conflict: oft he turned to the barrow,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sought for the gem-cup;<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005653\">7</$link></sup> this he soon perceived then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The dragon perceives that some one has disturbed his treasure.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">80</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That some man or other had discovered the gold,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The famous folk-treasure. Not fain did the hoard-ward</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wait until evening; then the ward of the barrow</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Was angry in spirit, the loathèd one wished to</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Pay for the dear-valued drink-cup with fire.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">85</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then the day was done as the dragon would have it,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He no longer would wait on the wall, but departed</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The dragon is infuriated.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fire-impelled, flaming. Fearful the start was</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To earls in the land, as it early thereafter</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To their giver-of-gold was grievously ended.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005500\">[1]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">long-gestréona</span>,’ B. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">láengestréona</span>,’ and renders, <i>Of fleeting treasures</i>. S. accepts H.’s ‘<span class=\"ang\">long-gestréona</span>,<span class=\"add\">’</span> but renders, <i>The treasure long in accumulating</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005508\">[2]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">hard-fyrdne</span>’ (2246), B. first suggested ‘<span class=\"ang\">hard-fyndne</span>,’ rendering: <i>A heap of treasures … so great that its equal would be hard to find</i>. The same scholar suggests later ‘<span class=\"ang\">hord-wynne dæl</span>’ = <i>A deal of treasure-joy</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005510\">[3]</$link> Some read ‘<span class=\"ang\">fec-word</span>’ (2247), and render: <i>Banning words uttered</i><span class=\"add\">.</span></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005568\">[4]</$link> An earlier reading of H.’s gave the following meaning to this passage: <i>He is said to inhabit a mound under the earth, where he, etc.</i> The translation in the text is more authentic.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005584\">[5]</$link> The repetition of ‘<span class=\"ang\">hord</span>’ in this passage has led some scholars to suggest new readings to avoid the second ‘<span class=\"ang\">hord</span>.’ This, however, is not under the main stress, and, it seems to me, might easily be accepted.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005614\">[6]</$link> The reading of H.-So. is well defended in the notes to that volume. B. emends and renders: <i>Nor was there any man in that desert who rejoiced in conflict, in battle-work.</i> That is, the hoard-ward could not find any one who had disturbed his slumbers, for no warrior was there, t.B.’s emendation would give substantially the same translation.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005618\">[7]</$link> ‘<span class=\"ang\">Sinc-fæt</span>’ (2301): this word both here and in v. 2232, t.B. renders ‘treasure.’</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2 class=\"num\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000123\">XXXIII.</$link></h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>BRAVE THOUGH AGED.—REMINISCENCES.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The dragon spits fire.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The stranger began then to vomit forth fire,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To burn the great manor; the blaze then glimmered</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For anguish to earlmen, not anything living</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Was the hateful air-goer willing to leave there.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The war of the worm widely was noticed,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The feud of the foeman afar and anear,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">How the enemy injured the earls of the Geatmen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Harried with hatred: back he hied to the treasure,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To the well-hidden cavern ere the coming of daylight.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He had circled with fire the folk of those regions,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With brand and burning; in the barrow he trusted,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In the wall and his war-might: the weening deceived him.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf hears of the havoc wrought by the dragon.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then straight was the horror to Beowulf published,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Early forsooth, that his own native homestead,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005815\">1</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The best of buildings, was burning and melting,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gift-seat of Geatmen. ’Twas a grief to the spirit</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of the good-mooded hero, the greatest of sorrows:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">He fears that Heaven is punishing him for some crime.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The wise one weened then that wielding his kingdom</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Gainst the ancient commandments, he had bitterly angered</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The Lord everlasting: with lorn meditations</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His bosom welled inward, as was nowise his custom.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The fire-spewing dragon fully had wasted</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The fastness of warriors, the water-land outward,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The manor with fire. The folk-ruling hero,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Prince of the Weders, was planning to wreak him.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The warmen’s defender bade them to make him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Earlmen’s atheling, an excellent war-shield</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">He orders an iron shield to be made from him, wood is useless.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wholly of iron: fully he knew then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That wood from the forest was helpless to aid him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Shield against fire. The long-worthy ruler</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Must live the last of his limited earth-days,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of life in the world and the worm along with him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Though he long had been holding hoard-wealth in plenty.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">He determines to fight alone.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then the ring-prince disdained to seek with a war-band,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With army extensive, the air-going ranger;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He felt no fear of the foeman’s assaults and</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He counted for little the might of the dragon,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His power and prowess: for previously dared he</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf’s early triumphs referred to</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A heap of hostility, hazarded dangers,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">War-thane, when Hrothgar’s palace he cleansèd,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Conquering combatant, clutched in the battle</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The kinsmen of Grendel, of kindred detested.<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005817\">2</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Higelac’s death recalled.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Twas of hand-fights not least where Higelac was slaughtered,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When the king of the Geatmen with clashings of battle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Friend-lord of folks in Frisian dominions,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Offspring of Hrethrel perished through sword-drink,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With battle-swords beaten; thence Beowulf came then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">On self-help relying, swam through the waters;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He bare on his arm, lone-going, thirty</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Outfits of armor, when the ocean he mounted.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The Hetwars by no means had need to be boastful</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of their fighting afoot, who forward to meet him</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Carried their war-shields: not many returned from</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The brave-mooded battle-knight back to their homesteads.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Ecgtheow’s bairn o’er the bight-courses swam then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Lone-goer lorn to his land-folk returning,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Where Hygd to him tendered treasure and kingdom,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Heardred’s lack of capacity to rule.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Rings and dominion: her son she not trusted,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To be able to keep the kingdom devised him</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Gainst alien races, on the death of King Higelac.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf’s tact and delicacy recalled.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Yet the sad ones succeeded not in persuading the atheling</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In any way ever, to act as a suzerain</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To Heardred, or promise to govern the kingdom;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Yet with friendly counsel in the folk he sustained him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gracious, with honor, till he grew to be older,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Reference is here made to a visit which Beowulf receives from Eanmund and Eadgils, why they come is not known.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wielded the Weders. Wide-fleeing outlaws,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Ohthere’s sons, sought him o’er the waters:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">They had stirred a revolt ’gainst the helm of the Scylfings,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The best of the sea-kings, who in Swedish dominions</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">70</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Distributed treasure, distinguished folk-leader.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Twas the end of his earth-days; injury fatal<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005819\">3</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">By swing of the sword he received as a greeting,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Offspring of Higelac; Ongentheow’s bairn</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Later departed to visit his homestead,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">75</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When Heardred was dead; let Beowulf rule them,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Govern the Geatmen: good was that folk-king.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005688\">[1]</$link> ‘<span class=\"ang\">Hám</span>’ (2326), the suggestion of B. is accepted by t.B. and other scholars.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005744\">[2]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">láðan cynnes</span>’ (2355), t.B. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">láðan cynne</span>,’ apposition to ‘<span class=\"ang\">mægum</span>.’ From syntactical and other considerations, this is a most excellent emendation.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005818",
