            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2 class=\"num\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000127\">XXXIV.</$link></h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>BEOWULF SEEKS THE DRAGON.—BEOWULF’S REMINISCENCES.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He planned requital for the folk-leader’s ruin</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In days thereafter, to Eadgils the wretched</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Becoming an enemy. Ohthere’s son then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Went with a war-troop o’er the wide-stretching currents</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With warriors and weapons: with woe-journeys cold he</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">After avenged him, the king’s life he took.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf has been preserved through many perils.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">So he came off uninjured from all of his battles,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Perilous fights, offspring of Ecgtheow,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">From his deeds of daring, till that day most momentous</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When he fate-driven fared to fight with the dragon.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">With eleven comrades, he seeks the dragon.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With eleven companions the prince of the Geatmen</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Went lowering with fury to look at the fire-drake:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Inquiring he’d found how the feud had arisen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hate to his heroes; the highly-famed gem-vessel</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Was brought to his keeping through the hand of th’ informer.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">A guide leads the way, but</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That in the throng was thirteenth of heroes,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That caused the beginning of conflict so bitter,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Captive and wretched, must sad-mooded thenceward</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">very reluctantly.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Point out the place: he passed then unwillingly</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To the spot where he knew of the notable cavern,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The cave under earth, not far from the ocean,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The anger of eddies, which inward was full of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Jewels and wires: a warden uncanny,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Warrior weaponed, wardered the treasure,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Old under earth; no easy possession</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For any of earth-folk access to get to.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then the battle-brave atheling sat on the naze-edge,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">While the gold-friend of Geatmen gracious saluted</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His fireside-companions: woe was his spirit,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Death-boding, wav’ring; Weird very near him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who must seize the old hero, his soul-treasure look for,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Dragging aloof his life from his body:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Not flesh-hidden long was the folk-leader’s spirit.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Beowulf spake, Ecgtheow’s son:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf’s retrospect.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“I survived in my youth-days many a conflict,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hours of onset: that all I remember.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I was seven-winters old when the jewel-prince took me,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">High-lord of heroes, at the hands of my father,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hrethel the hero-king had me in keeping,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Hrethel took me when I was seven.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gave me treasure and feasting, our kinship remembered;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Not ever was I <i>any</i> less dear to him</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">He treated me as a son.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Knight in the boroughs, than the bairns of his household,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Herebald and Hæthcyn and Higelac mine.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To the eldest unjustly by acts of a kinsman</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Was murder-bed strewn, since him Hæthcyn from horn-bow</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">One of the brothers accidentally kills another.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His sheltering chieftain shot with an arrow,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Erred in his aim and injured his kinsman,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">One brother the other, with blood-sprinkled spear:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">No fee could compound for such a calamity.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Twas a feeless fight, finished in malice,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sad to his spirit; the folk-prince however</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Had to part from existence with vengeance untaken.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">[A parallel case is supposed.]</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">So to hoar-headed hero ’tis heavily crushing<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005961\">1</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To live to see his son as he rideth</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Young on the gallows: then measures he chanteth,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A song of sorrow, when his son is hanging</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For the raven’s delight, and aged and hoary</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He is unable to offer any assistance.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Every morning his offspring’s departure</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Is constant recalled: he cares not to wait for</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The birth of an heir in his borough-enclosures,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Since that one through death-pain the deeds hath experienced.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He heart-grieved beholds in the house of his son the</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wine-building wasted, the wind-lodging places</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Reaved of their roaring; the riders are sleeping,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The knights in the grave; there’s no sound of the harp-wood,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Joy in the yards, as of yore were familiar.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005930\">[1]</$link> ‘<span class=\"ang\">Gomelum ceorle</span>’ (2445).—H. takes these words as referring to Hrethel; but the translator here departs from his editor by understanding the poet to refer to a hypothetical old man, introduced as an illustration of a father’s sorrow.\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p>Hrethrel had certainly never seen a son of his ride on the gallows to feed the crows.</p></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p>The passage beginning ‘<span class=\"ang\">swá bið géomorlic</span>’ seems to be an effort to reach a full simile, ‘as … so.’ ‘As it is mournful for an old man, etc. … so the defence of the Weders (2463) bore heart-sorrow, etc.’ The verses 2451 to 2463½ would be parenthetical, the poet’s feelings being so strong as to interrupt the simile. The punctuation of the fourth edition would be better—a comma after ‘<span class=\"ang\">galgan</span>’ (2447). The translation may be indicated as follows: <i>(Just) as it is sad for an old man to see his son ride young on the gallows when he himself is uttering mournful measures, a sorrowful song, while his son hangs for a comfort to the raven, and he, old and infirm, cannot render him any kelp—(he is constantly reminded, etc., 2451-2463)—so the defence of the Weders, etc.</i></p></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005966",
