        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“He seeks then his chamber, singeth a woe-song</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">One for the other; all too extensive</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Seemed homesteads and plains. So the helm of the Weders</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Hrethel grieves for Herebald.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Mindful of Herebald heart-sorrow carried,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Stirred with emotion, nowise was able</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To wreak his ruin on the ruthless destroyer:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He was unable to follow the warrior with hatred,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With deeds that were direful, though dear he not held him.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then pressed by the pang this pain occasioned him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He gave up glee, God-light elected;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He left to his sons, as the man that is rich does,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His land and fortress, when from life he departed.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Strife between Swedes and Geats.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000005999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then was crime and hostility ’twixt Swedes and Geatmen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">O’er wide-stretching water warring was mutual,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Burdensome hatred, when Hrethel had perished,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And Ongentheow’s offspring were active and valiant,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wished not to hold to peace oversea, but</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Round Hreosna-beorh often accomplished</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Cruelest massacre. This my kinsman avengèd,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The feud and fury, as ’tis found on inquiry,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Though one of them paid it with forfeit of life-joys,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Hæthcyn’s fall at Ravenswood.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With price that was hard: the struggle became then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fatal to Hæthcyn, lord of the Geatmen.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then I heard that at morning one brother the other</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With edges of irons egged on to murder,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Where Ongentheow maketh onset on Eofor:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The helmet crashed, the hoary-haired Scylfing</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sword-smitten fell, his hand then remembered</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Feud-hate sufficient, refused not the death-blow.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">I requited him for the jewels he gave me.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The gems that he gave me, with jewel-bright sword I</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Quited in contest, as occasion was offered:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Land he allowed me, life-joy at homestead,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Manor to live on. Little he needed</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">From Gepids or Danes or in Sweden to look for</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Trooper less true, with treasure to buy him;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Mong foot-soldiers ever in front I would hie me,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Alone in the vanguard, and evermore gladly</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Warfare shall wage, while this weapon endureth</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That late and early often did serve me</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf refers to his having slain Dæghrefn.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When I proved before heroes the slayer of Dæghrefn,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Knight of the Hugmen: he by no means was suffered</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To the king of the Frisians to carry the jewels,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The breast-decoration; but the banner-possessor</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bowed in the battle, brave-mooded atheling.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">No weapon was slayer, but war-grapple broke then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The surge of his spirit, his body destroying.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Now shall weapon’s edge make war for the treasure,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And hand and firm-sword.” Beowulf spake then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Boast-words uttered—the latest occasion:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">He boasts of his youthful prowess, and declares himself still fearless.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“I braved in my youth-days battles unnumbered;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Still am I willing the struggle to look for,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fame-deeds perform, folk-warden prudent,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">If the hateful despoiler forth from his cavern</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Seeketh me out!” Each of the heroes,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Helm-bearers sturdy, he thereupon greeted</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">His last salutations.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Belovèd co-liegemen—his last salutation:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“No brand would I bear, no blade for the dragon,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wist I a way my word-boast to ’complish<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006246\">1</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Else with the monster, as with Grendel I did it;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">But fire in the battle hot I expect there,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Furious flame-burning: so I fixed on my body</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Target and war-mail. The ward of the barrow<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006248\">2</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I’ll not flee from a foot-length, the foeman uncanny.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">At the wall ’twill befall us as Fate decreeth,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Let Fate decide between us.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Each one’s Creator. I am eager in spirit,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With the wingèd war-hero to away with all boasting.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bide on the barrow with burnies protected,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wait ye here till the battle is over.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Earls in armor, which of <i>us</i> two may better</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bear his disaster, when the battle is over.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">70</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Tis no matter of yours, and man cannot do it,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">But me and me only, to measure his strength with</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The monster of malice, might-deeds to ’complish.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I with prowess shall gain the gold, or the battle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Direful death-woe will drag off your ruler!”</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">75</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The mighty champion rose by his shield then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Brave under helmet, in battle-mail went he</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Neath steep-rising stone-cliffs, the strength he relied on</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of one man alone: no work for a coward.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then he saw by the wall who a great many battles</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">80</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Had lived through, most worthy, when foot-troops collided,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The place of strife is described.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Stone-arches standing, stout-hearted champion,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Saw a brook from the barrow bubbling out thenceward:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The flood of the fountain was fuming with war-flame:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Not nigh to the hoard, for season the briefest</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">85</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Could he brave, without burning, the abyss that was yawning,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The drake was so fiery. The prince of the Weders</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Caused then that words came from his bosom,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">So fierce was his fury; the firm-hearted shouted:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His battle-clear voice came in resounding</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">90</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Neath the gray-colored stone. Stirred was his hatred,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf calls out under the stone arches.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The hoard-ward distinguished the speech of a man;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Time was no longer to look out for friendship.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The breath of the monster issued forth first,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Vapory war-sweat, out of the stone-cave:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The terrible encounter.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">95</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The earth re-echoed. The earl ’neath the barrow</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Lifted his shield, lord of the Geatmen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Tow’rd the terrible stranger: the ring-twisted creature’s</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Heart was then ready to seek for a struggle.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf brandishes his sword,</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The excellent battle-king first brandished his weapon,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">100</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The ancient heirloom, of edges unblunted,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006250\">3</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To the death-planners twain was terror from other.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">and stands against his shield.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The lord of the troopers intrepidly stood then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Gainst his high-rising shield, when the dragon coiled him</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The dragon coils himself.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Quickly together: in corslet he bided.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"linenum\">105</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He went then in blazes, bended and striding,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hasting him forward. His life and body</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The targe well protected, for time-period shorter</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Than wish demanded for the well-renowned leader,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Where he then for the first day was forced to be victor,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">110</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Famous in battle, as Fate had not willed it.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The lord of the Geatmen uplifted his hand then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Smiting the fire-drake with sword that was precious,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That bright on the bone the blade-edge did weaken,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bit more feebly than his folk-leader needed,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">115</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Burdened with bale-griefs. Then the barrow-protector,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The dragon rages</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When the sword-blow had fallen, was fierce in his spirit,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Flinging his fires, flamings of battle</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gleamed then afar: the gold-friend of Weders</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf’s sword fails him.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Boasted no conquests, his battle-sword failed him</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">120</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Naked in conflict, as by no means it ought to,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Long-trusty weapon. ’Twas no slight undertaking</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That Ecgtheow’s famous offspring would leave</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The drake-cavern’s bottom; he must live in some region</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Other than this, by the will of the dragon,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">125</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As each one of earthmen existence must forfeit.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Twas early thereafter the excellent warriors</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The combat is renewed.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Met with each other. Anew and afresh</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The hoard-ward took heart (gasps heaved then his bosom):</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The great hero is reduced to extremities.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sorrow he suffered encircled with fire</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">130</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who the people erst governed. His companions by no means</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Were banded about him, bairns of the princes,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">His comrades flee!</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With valorous spirit, but they sped to the forest,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Seeking for safety. The soul-deeps of one were</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Blood is thicker than water.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Ruffled by care: kin-love can never</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">135</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Aught in him waver who well doth consider.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006089\">[1]</$link> The clause 2520(2)-2522(1), rendered by ‘Wist I … monster,’ Gr., followed by S., translates substantially as follows: <i>If I knew how else I might combat the boastful defiance of the monster</i>.—The translation turns upon ‘<span class=\"ang\">wiðgrípan</span>,’ a word not understood.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006097\">[2]</$link> B. emends and translates: <i>I will not flee the space of a foot from the guard of the barrow, but there shall be to us a fight at the wall, as fate decrees, each one’s Creator.</i></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006173\">[3]</$link> The translation of this passage is based on ‘<span class=\"ang\">unsláw</span>’ (2565), accepted by H.-So., in lieu of the long-standing ‘<span class=\"ang\">ungléaw</span>.’ The former is taken as an adj. limiting ‘<span class=\"ang\">sweord</span>’; the latter as an adj. c. ‘<span class=\"ang\">gúð-cyning</span>’: <i>The good war-king, rash with edges, brandished his sword, his old relic.</i> The latter gives a more rhetorical Anglo-Saxon (poetical) sentence.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2 class=\"num\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000135\">XXXVI.</$link></h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>WIGLAF THE TRUSTY.—BEOWULF IS DESERTED BY FRIENDS AND BY SWORD.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wiglaf remains true—the ideal Teutonic liegeman.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The son of Weohstan was Wiglaf entitled,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Shield-warrior precious, prince of the Scylfings,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Ælfhere’s kinsman: he saw his dear liegelord</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Enduring the heat ’neath helmet and visor.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then he minded the holding that erst he had given him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wiglaf recalls Beowulf’s generosity.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The Wægmunding warriors’ wealth-blessèd homestead,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Each of the folk-rights his father had wielded;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He was hot for the battle, his hand seized the target,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The yellow-bark shield, he unsheathed his old weapon,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Which was known among earthmen as the relic of Eanmund,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Ohthere’s offspring, whom, exiled and friendless,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Weohstan did slay with sword-edge in battle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And carried his kinsman the clear-shining helmet,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The ring-made burnie, the old giant-weapon</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That Onela gave him, his boon-fellow’s armor,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Ready war-trappings: he the feud did not mention,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Though he’d fatally smitten the son of his brother.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Many a half-year held he the treasures,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The bill and the burnie, till his bairn became able,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Like his father before him, fame-deeds to ’complish;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then he gave him ’mong Geatmen a goodly array of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Weeds for his warfare; he went from life then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Old on his journey. ’Twas the earliest time then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">This is Wiglaf’s first battle as liegeman of Beowulf.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That the youthful champion might charge in the battle</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Aiding his liegelord; his spirit was dauntless.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Nor did kinsman’s bequest quail at the battle:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">This the dragon discovered on their coming together.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wiglaf uttered many a right-saying,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Said to his fellows, sad was his spirit:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wiglaf appeals to the pride of the cowards.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“I remember the time when, tasting the mead-cup,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">We promised in the hall the lord of us all</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who gave us these ring-treasures, that this battle-equipment,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Swords and helmets, we’d certainly quite him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Should need of such aid ever befall him:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">How we have forfeited our liegelord’s confidence!</span> <span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In the war-band he chose us for this journey spontaneously,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Stirred us to glory and gave me these jewels,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Since he held and esteemed us trust-worthy spearmen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hardy helm-bearers, though this hero-achievement</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Our lord intended alone to accomplish,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Ward of his people, for most of achievements,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Doings audacious, he did among earth-folk.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Our lord is in sore need of us.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The day is now come when the ruler of earthmen</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Needeth the vigor of valiant heroes:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Let us wend us towards him, the war-prince to succor,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">While the heat yet rageth, horrible fire-fight.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">I would rather die than go home with out my suzerain.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">God wot in me, ’tis mickle the liefer</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The blaze should embrace my body and eat it</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With my treasure-bestower. Meseemeth not proper</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To bear our battle-shields back to our country,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Less first we are able to fell and destroy the</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Long-hating foeman, to defend the life of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Surely he does not deserve to die alone.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The prince of the Weders. Well do I know ’tisn’t</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Earned by his exploits, he only of Geatmen</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sorrow should suffer, sink in the battle:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Brand and helmet to us both shall be common,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\"><sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006436\">1</$link></sup>Shield-cover, burnie.” Through the bale-smoke he stalked then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Went under helmet to the help of his chieftain,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wiglaf reminds Beowulf of his youthful boasts.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Briefly discoursing: “Beowulf dear,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Perform thou all fully, as thou formerly saidst,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In thy youthful years, that while yet thou livedst</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Thou wouldst let thine honor not ever be lessened.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Thy life thou shalt save, mighty in actions,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Atheling undaunted, with all of thy vigor;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The monster advances on them.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I’ll give thee assistance.” The dragon came raging,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wild-mooded stranger, when these words had been uttered</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">(’Twas the second occasion), seeking his enemies,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Men that were hated, with hot-gleaming fire-waves;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With blaze-billows burned the board to its edges:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The fight-armor failed then to furnish assistance</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">70</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To the youthful spear-hero: but the young-agèd stripling</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Quickly advanced ’neath his kinsman’s war-target,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Since his own had been ground in the grip of the fire.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf strikes at the dragon.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then the warrior-king was careful of glory,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He soundly smote with sword-for-the-battle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">75</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That it stood in the head by hatred <span class=\"corr\">driven</span>;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Nægling was shivered, the old and iron-made</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">His sword fails him.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Brand of Beowulf in battle deceived him.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Twas denied him that edges of irons were able</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To help in the battle; the hand was too mighty</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">80</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\"><sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006438\">2</$link></sup>Which every weapon, as I heard on inquiry,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Outstruck in its stroke, when to struggle he carried</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The wonderful war-sword: it waxed him no better.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The dragon advances on Beowulf again.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then the people-despoiler—third of his onsets—</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fierce-raging fire-drake, of feud-hate was mindful,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">85</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Charged on the strong one, when chance was afforded,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Heated and war-grim, seized on his neck</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With teeth that were bitter; he bloody did wax with</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Soul-gore seething; sword-blood in waves boiled.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006369\">[1]</$link> The passage ‘<i>Brand … burnie</i>,’ is much disputed. In the first place, some eminent critics assume a gap of at least two half-verses.—‘<span class=\"ang\">Úrum</span>’ (2660), being a peculiar form, has been much discussed. ‘<span class=\"ang\">Byrdu-scrúd</span>’ is also a crux. B. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">býwdu-scrúd</span>’ = <i>splendid vestments</i>. Nor is ‘<span class=\"ang\">bám</span>’ accepted by all, ‘<span class=\"ang\">béon</span>’ being suggested. Whatever the individual words, the passage must mean, “<i>I intend to share with him my equipments of defence</i>.”</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006417\">[2]</$link> B. would render: <i>Which, as I heard, excelled in stroke every sword that he carried to the strife, even the strongest (sword).</i> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">Þonne</span>’ he reads ‘<span class=\"ang\">Þone</span>,’ rel. pr.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2 class=\"num\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000139\">XXXVII.</$link></h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>THE FATAL STRUGGLE.—BEOWULF’S LAST MOMENTS.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wiglaf defends Beowulf.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then I heard that at need of the king of the people</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The upstanding earlman exhibited prowess,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Vigor and courage, as suited his nature;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\"><sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006560\">1</$link></sup>He his head did not guard, but the high-minded liegeman’s</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hand was consumed, when he succored his kinsman,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">So he struck the strife-bringing strange-comer lower,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Earl-thane in armor, that <i>in</i> went the weapon</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gleaming and plated, that ’gan then the fire<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006562\">2</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf draws his knife,</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Later to lessen. The liegelord himself then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Retained his consciousness, brandished his war-knife,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Battle-sharp, bitter, that he bare on his armor:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">and cuts the dragon.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The Weder-lord cut the worm in the middle.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">They had felled the enemy (life drove out then<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006564\">3</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Puissant prowess), the pair had destroyed him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Land-chiefs related: so a liegeman should prove him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A thaneman when needed. To the prince ’twas the last of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His era of conquest by his own great achievements,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf’s wound swells and burns.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The latest of world-deeds. The wound then began</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Which the earth-dwelling dragon erstwhile had wrought him</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To burn and to swell. He soon then discovered</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That bitterest bale-woe in his bosom was raging,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Poison within. The atheling advanced then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">He sits down exhausted.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That along by the wall, he prudent of spirit</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Might sit on a settle; he saw the giant-work,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">How arches of stone strengthened with pillars</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The earth-hall eternal inward supported.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then the long-worthy liegeman laved with his hand the</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wiglaf bathes his lord’s head.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Far-famous chieftain, gory from sword-edge,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Refreshing the face of his friend-lord and ruler,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sated with battle, unbinding his helmet.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Beowulf answered, of his injury spake he,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His wound that was fatal (he was fully aware</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He had lived his allotted life-days enjoying</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The pleasures of earth; then past was entirely</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His measure of days, death very near):</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf regrets that he has no son.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“My son I would give now my battle-equipments,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Had any of heirs been after me granted,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Along of my body. This people I governed</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fifty of winters: no king ’mong my neighbors</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Dared to encounter me with comrades-in-battle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Try me with terror. The time to me ordered</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I bided at home, mine own kept fitly,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sought me no snares, swore me not many</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">I can rejoice in a well-spent life.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Oaths in injustice. Joy over all this</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I’m able to have, though ill with my death-wounds;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hence the Ruler of Earthmen need not charge me</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With the killing of kinsmen, when cometh my life out</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Forth from my body. Fare thou with haste now</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Bring me the hoard, Wiglaf, that my dying eyes may be refreshed by a sight of it.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To behold the hoard ’neath the hoar-grayish stone,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Well-lovèd Wiglaf, now the worm is a-lying,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sore-wounded sleepeth, disseized of his treasure.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Go thou in haste that treasures of old I,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gold-wealth may gaze on, together see lying</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The ether-bright jewels, be easier able,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Having the heap of hoard-gems, to yield my</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Life and the land-folk whom long I have governed.”</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006453\">[1]</$link> B. renders: <i>He</i> (<i>W</i>.) did not regard his (<i>the dragon’s</i>) <i>head</i> (since Beowulf had struck it without effect), <i>but struck the dragon a little lower down.—</i>One crux is to find out <i>whose head</i> is meant; another is to bring out the antithesis between ‘head’ and ‘hand.’</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006461\">[2]</$link> ‘<span class=\"ang\">Þæt þæt fýr</span>’ (2702), S. emends to ‘<span class=\"ang\">þá þæt fýr</span>’ = <i>when the fire began to grow less intense afterward</i>. This emendation relieves the passage of a plethora of conjunctive <i>þæt</i>’s.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006471\">[3]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">gefyldan</span>’ (2707), S. proposes ‘<span class=\"ang\">gefylde</span>.’ The passage would read: <i>He felled the foe (life drove out strength), and they then both had destroyed him, chieftains related</i>. This gives Beowulf the credit of having felled the dragon; then they combine to annihilate him.—For ‘<span class=\"ang\">ellen</span>’ (2707), Kl. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">e(a)llne</span>.’—The reading ‘<i>life drove out strength</i>’ is very unsatisfactory and very peculiar. I would suggest as follows: Adopt S.’s emendation, remove H.’s parenthesis, read ‘<span class=\"ang\">ferh-ellen wræc</span>,’ and translate: <i>He felled the foe, drove out his life-strength</i> (that is, made him <i>hors de combat</i>), <i>and then they both, etc</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
