            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2 class=\"num\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000143\">XXXVIII.</$link></h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>WIGLAF PLUNDERS THE DRAGON’S DEN.—BEOWULF’S DEATH.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wiglaf fulfils his lord’s behest.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then heard I that Wihstan’s son very quickly,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">These words being uttered, heeded his liegelord</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wounded and war-sick, went in his armor,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His well-woven ring-mail, ’neath the roof of the barrow.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then the trusty retainer treasure-gems many</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The dragon’s den.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Victorious saw, when the seat he came near to,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gold-treasure sparkling spread on the bottom,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wonder on the wall, and the worm-creature’s cavern,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The ancient dawn-flier’s, vessels a-standing,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Cups of the ancients of cleansers bereavèd,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Robbed of their ornaments: there were helmets in numbers,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Old and rust-eaten, arm-bracelets many,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Artfully woven. Wealth can easily,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gold on the sea-bottom, turn into vanity<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006708\">1</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Each one of earthmen, arm him who pleaseth!</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And he saw there lying an all-golden banner</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">High o’er the hoard, of hand-wonders greatest,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Linkèd with lacets: a light from it sparkled,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That the floor of the cavern he was able to look on,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The dragon is not there.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To examine the jewels. Sight of the dragon</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Not any was offered, but edge offcarried him.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wiglaf bears the hoard away.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then I heard that the hero the hoard-treasure plundered,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The giant-work ancient reaved in the cavern,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bare on his bosom the beakers and platters,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As himself would fain have it, and took off the standard,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The brightest of beacons;<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006710\">2</$link></sup> the bill had erst injured</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">(Its edge was of iron), the old-ruler’s weapon,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Him who long had watched as ward of the jewels,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who fire-terror carried hot for the treasure,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Rolling in battle, in middlemost darkness,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Till murdered he perished. The messenger hastened,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Not loth to return, hurried by jewels:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Curiosity urged him if, excellent-mooded,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Alive he should find the lord of the Weders</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Mortally wounded, at the place where he left him.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Mid the jewels he found then the famous old chieftain,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His liegelord belovèd, at his life’s-end gory:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He thereupon ’gan to lave him with water,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Till the point of his word piercèd his breast-hoard.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Beowulf spake (the gold-gems he noticed),</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Beowulf is rejoiced to see the jewels.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The old one in sorrow: “For the jewels I look on</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Thanks do I utter for all to the Ruler,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wielder of Worship, with words of devotion,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The Lord everlasting, that He let me such treasures</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gain for my people ere death overtook me.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Since I’ve bartered the agèd life to me granted</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For treasure of jewels, attend ye henceforward</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">He desires to be held in memory by his people.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The wants of the war-thanes; I can wait here no longer.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The battle-famed bid ye to build them a grave-hill,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bright when I’m burned, at the brim-current’s limit;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As a memory-mark to the men I have governed,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Aloft it shall tower on Whale’s-Ness uprising,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That earls of the ocean hereafter may call it</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Beowulf’s barrow, those who barks ever-dashing</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">From a distance shall drive o’er the darkness of waters.”</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The hero’s last gift</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The bold-mooded troop-lord took from his neck then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The ring that was golden, gave to his liegeman,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The youthful war-hero, his gold-flashing helmet,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His collar and war-mail, bade him well to enjoy them:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">and last words.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“Thou art latest left of the line of our kindred,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of Wægmunding people: Weird hath offcarried</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">All of my kinsmen to the Creator’s glory,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Earls in their vigor: I shall after them fare.”</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Twas the aged liegelord’s last-spoken word in</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His musings of spirit, ere he mounted the fire,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The battle-waves burning: from his bosom departed</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His soul to seek the sainted ones’ glory.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006599\">[1]</$link> The word ‘<span class=\"ang\">oferhígian</span>’ (2767) being vague and little understood, two quite distinct translations of this passage have arisen. One takes ‘<span class=\"ang\">oferhígian</span>’ as meaning ‘to exceed,’ and, inserting ‘<span class=\"ang\">hord</span>’ after ‘<span class=\"ang\">gehwone</span>,’ renders: <i>The treasure may easily, the gold in the ground, exceed in value every hoard of man, hide it who will.</i> The other takes ‘<span class=\"ang\">oferhígian</span>’ as meaning ‘to render arrogant,’ and, giving the sentence a moralizing tone, renders substantially as in the body of this work. (Cf. <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000004773\">28 <span class=\"smaller\">13</span></$link> et seq.)</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006623\">[2]</$link> The passage beginning here is very much disputed. ‘The bill of the old lord’ is by some regarded as Beowulf’s sword; by others, as that of the ancient possessor of the hoard. ‘<span class=\"ang\">Ær gescód</span>’ (2778), translated in this work as verb and adverb, is by some regarded as a compound participial adj. = <i>sheathed in brass</i>.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2 class=\"num\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000147\">XXXIX.</$link></h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>THE DEAD FOES.—WIGLAF’S BITTER TAUNTS.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wiglaf is sorely grieved to see his lord look so un-warlike.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">It had wofully chanced then the youthful retainer</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To behold on earth the most ardent-belovèd</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">At his life-days’ limit, lying there helpless.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The slayer too lay there, of life all bereavèd,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Horrible earth-drake, harassed with sorrow:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The dragon has plundered his last hoard.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The round-twisted monster was permitted no longer</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To govern the ring-hoards, but edges of war-swords</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Mightily seized him, battle-sharp, sturdy</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Leavings of hammers, that still from his wounds</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The flier-from-farland fell to the earth</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hard by his hoard-house, hopped he at midnight</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Not e’er through the air, nor exulting in jewels</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Suffered them to see him: but he sank then to earthward</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Through the hero-chief’s handwork. I heard sure it throve then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"sidenote\">Few warriors dared to face the monster.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">But few in the land of liegemen of valor,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Though of every achievement bold he had proved him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To run ’gainst the breath of the venomous scather,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Or the hall of the treasure to trouble with hand-blows,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">If he watching had found the ward of the hoard-hall</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">On the barrow abiding. Beowulf’s part of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The treasure of jewels was paid for with death;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Each of the twain had attained to the end of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Life so unlasting. Not long was the time till</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The cowardly thanes come out of the thicket.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The tardy-at-battle returned from the thicket,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The timid truce-breakers ten all together,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who durst not before play with the lances</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In the prince of the people’s pressing emergency;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">They are ashamed of their desertion.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">But blushing with shame, with shields they betook them,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With arms and armor where the old one was lying:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">They gazed upon Wiglaf. He was sitting exhausted,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Foot-going fighter, not far from the shoulders</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of the lord of the people, would rouse him with water;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">No whit did it help him; though he hoped for it keenly,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He was able on earth not at all in the leader</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Life to retain, and nowise to alter</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The will of the Wielder; the World-Ruler’s power<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006854\">1</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Would govern the actions of each one of heroes,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wiglaf is ready to excoriate them.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As yet He is doing. From the young one forthwith then</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Could grim-worded greeting be got for him quickly</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Whose courage had failed him. Wiglaf discoursed then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Weohstan his son, sad-mooded hero,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">He begins to taunt them.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Looked on the hated: “He who soothness will utter</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Can say that the liegelord who gave you the jewels,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The ornament-armor wherein ye are standing,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When on ale-bench often he offered to hall-men</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Helmet and burnie, the prince to his liegemen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">As best upon earth he was able to find him,—</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"sidenote\">Surely our lord wasted his armor on poltroons.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That he wildly wasted his war-gear undoubtedly</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When battle o’ertook him.<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006856\">2</$link></sup> The troop-king no need had</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To glory in comrades; yet God permitted him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">He, however, got along without you</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Victory-Wielder, with weapon unaided</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Himself to avenge, when vigor was needed.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">I life-protection but little was able</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To give him in battle, and I ’gan, notwithstanding,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">With some aid, I could have saved our liegelord</span> <span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Helping my kinsman (my strength overtaxing):</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He waxed the weaker when with weapon I smote on</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">My mortal opponent, the fire less strongly</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Flamed from his bosom. Too few of protectors</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Came round the king at the critical moment.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Gift-giving is over with your people: the ring-lord is dead.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Now must ornament-taking and weapon-bestowing,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Home-joyance all, cease for your kindred,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Food for the people; each of your warriors</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Must needs be bereavèd of rights that he holdeth</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In landed possessions, when faraway nobles</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Shall learn of your leaving your lord so basely,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">What is life without honor?</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The dastardly deed. Death is more pleasant</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To every earlman than infamous life is!”</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006789\">[1]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">dædum rædan</span>’ (2859) B. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">déað árædan</span>,’ and renders: <i>The might (or judgment) of God would determine death for every man, as he still does.</i></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006815\">[2]</$link> Some critics, H. himself in earlier editions, put the clause, ‘When … him’ (A.-S. ‘<span class=\"ang\">þá … beget</span>’) with the following sentence; that is, they make it dependent upon ‘<span class=\"ang\">þorfte</span>’ (2875) instead of upon ‘<span class=\"ang\">forwurpe</span>’ (2873).</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006858": {
