            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2 class=\"num\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000151\">XL.</$link></h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>THE MESSENGER OF DEATH.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wiglaf sends the news of Beowulf’s death to liegemen near by.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then he charged that the battle be announced at the hedge</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Up o’er the cliff-edge, where the earl-troopers bided</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The whole of the morning, mood-wretched sat them,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bearers of battle-shields, both things expecting,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The end of his lifetime and the coming again of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The liegelord belovèd. Little reserved he</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of news that was known, who the ness-cliff did travel,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">But he truly discoursed to all that could hear him:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"sidenote\">The messenger speaks.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“Now the free-giving friend-lord of the folk of the Weders,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The folk-prince of Geatmen, is fast in his death-bed,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">By the deeds of the dragon in death-bed abideth;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Along with him lieth his life-taking foeman</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Slain with knife-wounds: he was wholly unable</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To injure at all the ill-planning monster</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wiglaf sits by our dead lord.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With bite of his sword-edge. Wiglaf is sitting,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Offspring of Wihstan, up over Beowulf,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Earl o’er another whose end-day hath reached him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Head-watch holdeth o’er heroes unliving,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006967\">1</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Our lord’s death will lead to attacks from our old foes.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For friend and for foeman. The folk now expecteth</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A season of strife when the death of the folk-king</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To Frankmen and Frisians in far-lands is published.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The war-hatred waxed warm ’gainst the Hugmen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Higelac’s death recalled.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When Higelac came with an army of vessels</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Faring to Friesland, where the Frankmen in battle</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Humbled him and bravely with overmight ’complished</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That the mail-clad warrior must sink in the battle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fell ’mid his folk-troop: no fret-gems presented</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The atheling to earlmen; aye was denied us</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Merewing’s mercy. The men of the Swedelands</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">For truce or for truth trust I but little;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">But widely ’twas known that near Ravenswood Ongentheow</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Hæthcyn’s fall referred to.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sundered Hæthcyn the Hrethling from life-joys,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When for pride overweening the War-Scylfings first did</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Seek the Geatmen with savage intentions.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Early did Ohthere’s age-laden father,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Old and terrible, give blow in requital,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Killing the sea-king, the queen-mother rescued,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The old one his consort deprived of her gold,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Onela’s mother and Ohthere’s also,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And then followed the feud-nursing foemen till hardly,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Reaved of their ruler, they Ravenswood entered.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then with vast-numbered forces he assaulted the remnant,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Weary with wounds, woe often promised</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The livelong night to the sad-hearted war-troop:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Said he at morning would kill them with edges of weapons,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Some on the gallows for glee to the fowls.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Aid came after to the anxious-in-spirit</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">At dawn of the day, after Higelac’s bugle</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And trumpet-sound heard they, when the good one proceeded</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And faring followed the flower of the troopers.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006900\">[1]</$link> ‘<span class=\"ang\">Hige-méðum</span>’ (2910) is glossed by H. as dat. plu. (= for the dead). S. proposes ‘<span class=\"ang\">hige-méðe</span>,’ nom. sing. limiting Wigláf; i.e. <i>W., mood-weary, holds head-watch o’er friend and foe</i>.—B. suggests taking the word as dat. inst. plu. of an abstract noun in -‘u.’ The translation would be substantially the same as S.’s.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2 class=\"num\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000000153\">XLI.</$link></h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><h2>THE MESSENGER’S RETROSPECT.</h2></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The messenger continues, and refers to the feuds of Swedes and Geats.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">“The blood-stainèd trace of Swedes and Geatmen,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The death-rush of warmen, widely was noticed,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">How the folks with each other feud did awaken.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The worthy one went then<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007201\">1</$link></sup> with well-beloved comrades,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">5</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Old and dejected to go to the fastness,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Ongentheo earl upward then turned him;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Of Higelac’s battle he’d heard on inquiry,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The exultant one’s prowess, despaired of resistance,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With earls of the ocean to be able to struggle,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">10</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Gainst sea-going sailors to save the hoard-treasure,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His wife and his children; he fled after thenceward</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Old ’neath the earth-wall. Then was offered pursuance</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To the braves of the Swedemen, the banner<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007203\">2</$link></sup> to Higelac.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">They fared then forth o’er the field-of-protection,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">15</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When the Hrethling heroes hedgeward had thronged them.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then with edges of irons was Ongentheow driven,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The gray-haired to tarry, that the troop-ruler had to</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Suffer the power solely of Eofor:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Wulf wounds Ongentheow.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wulf then wildly with weapon assaulted him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">20</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wonred his son, that for swinge of the edges</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The blood from his body burst out in currents,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Forth ’neath his hair. He feared not however,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gray-headed Scylfing, but speedily quited</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Ongentheow gives a stout blow in return.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The wasting wound-stroke with worse exchange,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">25</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When the king of the thane-troop thither did turn him:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The wise-mooded son of Wonred was powerless</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To give a return-blow to the age-hoary man,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">But his head-shielding helmet first hewed he to pieces,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That flecked with gore perforce he did totter,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">30</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fell to the earth; not fey was he yet then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">But up did he spring though an edge-wound had reached him.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Eofor smites Ongentheow fiercely.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Then Higelac’s vassal, valiant and dauntless,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When his brother lay dead, made his broad-bladed weapon,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Giant-sword ancient, defence of the giants,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">35</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bound o’er the shield-wall; the folk-prince succumbed then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Ongentheow is slain.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Shepherd of people, was pierced to the vitals.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">There were many attendants who bound up his kinsman,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Carried him quickly when occasion was granted</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That the place of the slain they were suffered to manage.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">40</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">This pending, one hero plundered the other,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His armor of iron from Ongentheow ravished,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His hard-sword hilted and helmet together;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Eofor takes the old king’s war-gear to Higelac.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The old one’s equipments he carried to Higelac.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He the jewels received, and rewards ’mid the troopers</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">45</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Graciously promised, and so did accomplish:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The king of the Weders requited the war-rush,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hrethel’s descendant, when home he repaired him,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">Higelac rewards the brothers.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To Eofor and Wulf with wide-lavished treasures,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To each of them granted a hundred of thousands</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"linenum\">50</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In land and rings wrought out of wire:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">His gifts were beyond cavil.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">None upon mid-earth needed to twit him<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007205\">3</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With the gifts he gave them, when glory they conquered;</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">To Eofor he also gives his only daughter in marriage.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And to Eofor then gave he his one only daughter,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The honor of home, as an earnest of favor.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">55</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That’s the feud and hatred—as ween I ’twill happen—</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The anger of earthmen, that earls of the Swedemen</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Will visit on us, when they hear that our leader</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Lifeless is lying, he who longtime protected</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His hoard and kingdom ’gainst hating assailers,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">60</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who on the fall of the heroes defended of yore</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The deed-mighty Scyldings,<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007207\">4</$link></sup> did for the troopers</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">What best did avail them, and further moreover</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">It is time for us to pay the last marks of respect to our lord.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Hero-deeds ’complished. Now is haste most fitting,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That the lord of liegemen we look upon yonder,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">65</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And <i>that</i> one carry on journey to death-pyre</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Who ring-presents gave us. Not aught of it all</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Shall melt with the brave one—there’s a mass of bright jewels,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gold beyond measure, grewsomely purchased</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">And ending it all ornament-rings too</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">70</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Bought with his life; these fire shall devour,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Flame shall cover, no earlman shall wear</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A jewel-memento, nor beautiful virgin</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Have on her neck rings to adorn her,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">But wretched in spirit bereavèd of gold-gems</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">75</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">She shall oft with others be exiled and banished,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Since the leader of liegemen hath laughter forsaken,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Mirth and merriment. Hence many a war-spear</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Cold from the morning shall be clutched in the fingers,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Heaved in the hand, no harp-music’s sound shall</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">80</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Waken the warriors, but the wan-coated raven</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fain over fey ones freely shall gabble,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Shall say to the eagle how he sped in the eating,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">When, the wolf his companion, he plundered the slain.”</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">So the high-minded hero was rehearsing these stories</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">85</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Loathsome to hear; he lied as to few of</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The warriors go sadly to look at Beowulf’s lifeless body.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Weirds and of words. All the war-troop arose then,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">’Neath the Eagle’s Cape sadly betook them,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Weeping and woful, the wonder to look at.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">They saw on the sand then soulless a-lying,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">90</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">His slaughter-bed holding, him who rings had given them</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">In days that were done; then the death-bringing moment</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Was come to the good one, that the king very warlike,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Wielder of Weders, with wonder-death perished.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">First they beheld there a creature more wondrous,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">They also see the dragon.</span> <span class=\"linenum\">95</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The worm on the field, in front of them lying,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The foeman before them: the fire-spewing dragon,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Ghostly and grisly guest in his terrors,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Was scorched in the fire; as he lay there he measured</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Fifty of feet; came forth in the night-time<sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007209\">5</$link></sup></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">100</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To rejoice in the air, thereafter departing</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">To visit his den; he in death was then fastened,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">He would joy in no other earth-hollowed caverns.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">There stood round about him beakers and vessels,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Dishes were lying and dear-valued weapons,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"linenum\">105</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">With iron-rust eaten, as in earth’s mighty bosom</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">A thousand of winters there they had rested:</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">The hoard was under a magic spell.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">That mighty bequest then with magic was guarded,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Gold of the ancients, that earlman not any</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">The ring-hall could touch, save Ruling-God only,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> <span class=\"linenum\">110</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">Sooth-king of Vict’ries gave whom He wished to</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n<span class=\"sidenote\">God alone could give access to it.</span>\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\"><sup class=\"footnoteref\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007211\">6</$link></sup>(He is earth-folk’s protector) to open the treasure,</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"l\">E’en to such among mortals as seemed to Him proper.</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000006982\">[1]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">góda</span>,’ which seems a surprising epithet for a Geat to apply to the “terrible” Ongentheow, B. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">gomela</span>.’ The passage would then stand: ‘<i>The old one went then,’ etc.</i></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007000\">[2]</$link> For ‘<span class=\"ang\">segn Higeláce</span>,’ K., Th., and B. propose ‘<span class=\"ang\">segn Higeláces</span>,’ meaning: <i>Higelac’s banner followed the Swedes (in pursuit).</i>—S. suggests ‘<span class=\"ang\">sæcc Higeláces</span>,’ and renders: <i>Higelac’s pursuit.</i>—The H.-So. reading, as translated in our text, means that the banner of the enemy was captured and brought to Higelac as a trophy.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007076\">[3]</$link> The rendering given in this translation represents the king as being generous beyond the possibility of reproach; but some authorities construe ‘him’ (2996) as plu., and understand the passage to mean that no one reproached the two brothers with having received more reward than they were entitled to.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007096\">[4]</$link> The name ‘<span class=\"ang\">Scyldingas</span>’ here (3006) has caused much discussion, and given rise to several theories, the most important of which are as follows: (1) After the downfall of Hrothgar’s family, Beowulf was king of the Danes, or Scyldings. (2) For ‘<span class=\"ang\">Scyldingas</span>’ read ‘<span class=\"ang\">Scylfingas</span>’—that is, after killing Eadgils, the Scylfing prince, Beowulf conquered his land, and held it in subjection. (3) M. considers 3006 a thoughtless repetition of 2053. (Cf. H.-So.)</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007172\">[5]</$link> B. takes ‘<span class=\"ang\">nihtes</span>’ and ‘<span class=\"ang\">hwílum</span>’ (3045) as separate adverbial cases, and renders: <i>Joy in the air had he of yore by night, etc</i>. He thinks that the idea of vanished time ought to be expressed.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"div1 c12\"><div class=\"fit\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007196\">[6]</$link> The parenthesis is by some emended so as to read: (1) (<i>He</i> (i.e. <i>God</i>) <i>is the hope of men</i>); (2) (<i>he is the hope of heroes</i>). Gr.’s reading has no parenthesis, but says: … <i>could touch, unless God himself, true king of victories, gave to whom he would to open the treasure, the secret place of enchanters, etc</i>. The last is rejected on many grounds.</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b444daeafa3e6711/text/000007212",
