            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-0bfa64 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-e8bee0 twpub-b444daeafa3e6711-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"c13\">*** END OF THE PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK BEOWULF ***</div></div>"
